biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Kindness is a strength. 

Compassion is a strength. 

We are stronger as a country when we care for the vulnerable in our society. 

During this morning’s beautiful service at St Christopher’s Cathedral in Canberra, we had the chance to reflect on the reasons we have to be optimistic about the road ahead.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The new entrance at the Australian War Memorial is marked by a magnificent oculus. 

This is a place of light where Australians can reflect on the darkness of war. 

I hope every visitor to Canberra can make their way here to this magnificent building and pay tribute to those who made the ultimate sacrifice for our country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Creating opportunity for women is a matter of national interest and a driver of national success. Because when women get ahead, Australia moves forward.

Ahead of International Women’s Day, we reflect on how far we’ve come and the work still ahead.

In the last three years, we’ve made overdue changes: expanding Paid Parental Leave, delivering a 15% pay rise for early educators, strengthening protections against workplace harassment, and bringing the gender pay gap to an all-time low.

We’re taking action on violence against women - investing in crisis housing, supporting survivors, and focusing on prevention. 

And we’re driving change in child care, with a new 3-Day Guarantee to support Aussie families and make sure every child has access to quality early education. 

But there’s more to do. And we’ll keep working until fairness, safety, and opportunity are a reality for everyone in Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This matters.

We're delivering more endo and pelvic pain clinics, easier access to vital medicines at a lower cost, and more specialised Medicare support.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
In the worst of times we see the best of Australians. 

And in recent days, I’ve seen Australians helping one another in their time of need. 

This morning at the National Situation Room in Canberra, I received a briefing on the work underway to help those affected by the floods in northern Queensland. 

Places like Townsville and Ingham will remain under threat from floodwaters over the coming days.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
North Queenslanders are tough, but these are tough times with the region being hit hard by flooding. 

We're doing everything we can to help.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Generations were stolen.

Children were told they were unloved by their parents. 

They were punished for using their own names and language. 

And it happened here in Australia within living memory. 

17 years ago Kevin Rudd delivered the Apology to the Stolen Generations. 

Today we remember, and we commit as a country to heal – and to act – together.

We are making every effort, partnering with local communities to close the gap. 

We are building more houses, delivering healthcare, and making sure food is affordable in remote Aboriginal communities. 

We can do more. And we will.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Inflation is going down. Wages are going up. Unemployment is low.

After a tough few years, we’ve started 2025 with new reasons to be optimistic about the road ahead. 

There's more to do.

We're back in Parliament to make free TAFE permanent, guarantee three days of child care subsidy, keep the NBN in public hands and more.

We're building Australia's future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
National aerial assets are being deployed, and Australian Defence Force personnel are on the ground helping with everything from sandbagging to logistics.

The Federal Government and Qld Government have activated emergency funding for residents and councils.

We also have a heatwave stretching across the country from Western Australia to Tasmania, with bushfires still active in Victoria.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: And we pay tribute those who serve today.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Happy Lunar New Year 🧧
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
More tragic news from Queensland today, with police confirming a woman has died near Ingham in floodwaters.

I’m thinking of the family and the community during this incredibly difficult time.

We continue to work with the Queensland Government to assist, with whatever resources are required.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I want to thank each and every emergency service worker helping their fellow Australians in what is a difficult time for our country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We'll make sure North Queensland gets all the support it needs to get back on its feet.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Opportunity, safety, and genuine investment are key to healthy communities. 

That’s why we’re strengthening services in remote Aboriginal communities in the Northern Territory. 

Today's funding agreement with the NT Government and Aboriginal Peak Organisations NT will support local leadership. 

It's about creating jobs, and making sure families get the care and support they need from services like the Central Australian Aboriginal Congress here in Alice Springs. 

My Government remains determined to seek better results for Indigenous Australians to help Close the Gap.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today's headline inflation numbers are the lowest in nearly four years. That's welcome news for Australia. 

We know that the fight against inflation is not yet over - that’s why we'll keep working to tackle costs while supporting people.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Lest We Forget. 

Just three words, yet they hold with them a profound power and dignity. 

We come here before every parliamentary year in remembrance of and respect for the great debt we owe to our veterans.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australians are thinking of all those affected by the terrible air crash at Reagan Airport in Washington and the tragic loss of life. Our hearts go out to their families and loved ones. 

As first responders work at the scene, we encourage any Australians in need of assistance to contact the Australian Government’s 24-hour Consular Emergency Centre 1300 555 135 (within Australia) and +61 2 6261 3305 (from overseas).
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Great to catch up with Lord Mayor Nicholas Reece in this beautiful city.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Public schools change lives.

We're making sure Victorian children get the best start in life by fully funding every public school across the state.

It's the biggest new investment in Victorian public schools by any Australian Government - ever. 

And it will give every child the chance to reach their potential.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australians are deeply shocked by the shooting in Örebro, Sweden. 

Violence like this is as senseless as it is abhorrent, and our thoughts are with the victims and their loved ones.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Happy Australia Day everyone!
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Wishing all Australians celebrating a very happy Lunar New Year.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: And Australia’s Local Heroes for 2025, Vanessa Brettell and Hannah Costello co-founded Café Stepping Stone, a social enterprise empowering migrant and refugee women through employment and training.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Breaking news.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: NEWS: Aussie families have saved more than $2700 through child care subsidies.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Thanks to the Asian Business Association of Whitehorse for hosting this incredible event.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
International Holocaust Remembrance Day this year falls on the 80th anniversary of the liberation of Auschwitz-Birkenau. 

Hearing the stories of survivors today was deeply moving. We must keep their memories alive for future generations. 

My Government is investing in the National Holocaust Education Centre in Canberra, and the Holocaust Institute of WA’s Education Centre here at the JHub in Perth.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: NEWS: $10,000 extra cash to help new construction apprentices.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Education opens the doors of opportunity and changes lives.

Today we’re making sure that every child in public schools gets the support they need, with new schools funding agreements with South Australia and Victoria.

With six of the states and territories now signed up to the Better and Fairer Schools agreement, we’re investing in what works.

Early phonics and numeracy testing. Classroom assistants and targeted tutoring. Support for advanced learners. More help for teachers and individual attention for every child.

This is real reform, designed to deliver real results.

And we’ll keep working to make sure every Australian student has a world class education.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
These apprentices will help build the 1.2 million homes we're building to make housing more affordable.

We’re giving $10,000 cash to help apprentices become the carpenters, plumbers and sparkies we’ll need in the future. 

And we’re making free TAFE permanent.

This is what building Australia’s future looks like.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Xin nian kuai le.
Gong hei fat choy!

What a beautiful celebration in Box Hill in Melbourne. 

The contribution of the Chinese Australian community is something to celebrate every day of the year.

I will never take your community, or your contribution to our nation, for granted.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Introducing your 2025 Australian of the Year, Neale Daniher AO. 

After a decorated VFL/AFL career as a player and coach, in 2013, Neale was diagnosed with motor neurone disease. 

Neale’s battle against what he calls “the Beast” has brought new hope and inspiration into the lives of everyone affected by MND and it has won him the boundless admiration of all Australians.

Neale is a co-founder of FightMND which has raised over $100 million to fund vital research  and has made the “Big Freeze” an iconic part of the AFL season.

Neale’s extraordinary story is not about what MND has taken from him, it’s about all that Neale has given: to our awareness of this disease and to the cause of finding a cure.

Neale is fond of the saying “When all is said and done, more is said than done.” 

It is hard to think of anyone who has done more than Neale in the service of others.  

Congratulations to Neale and his remarkable family.

As Australian of the Year, Neale will inspire all Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Heartbreaking news out of Queensland today, with police confirming a woman has died in floodwaters in Ingham. 

My thoughts are with the family and the entire community at this awful time.  

The full support of the Queensland and Federal Governments is being deployed to assist with these floods.

I have spoken with Premier Crisafulli and reiterated we will supply whatever resources are required to deal with this event.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Labor governments build.  

In Western Australia, we're partnering with Premier @RogerCookMLA to upgrade the Kwinana Freeway. 

And it all leads here to support the Westport project, which is set to transform Fremantle and Kwinana.

Building Australia's future with more jobs in WA, and faster and safer journeys.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We’ve helped 200,000 Australians get into a home of their own with a low deposit.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: As we mark International Holocaust Remembrance Day on the 80th anniversary of the liberation of Auschwitz-Birkenau, our observance carries a powerful message about the enduring strength of the Jewish people, and about our unwavering commitment to combat antisemitism.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: National Cabinet met virtually today to reaffirm that Leaders are united in working together to stamp antisemitism out – and keep it out.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
“Completely nuts” is how Matthew Benns described his and Warren Brown’s latest adventure. 

They have just driven an actual 1925 Bean 14 car all the way from London to Melbourne. 

All the while raising money for the incredible work the Royal Flying Doctor Service does right across Australia. 

This very spot in Melbourne is where Francis Birtles finished his record-breaking journey back in 1927. 
 
I was proud to welcome Warren and Matthew back from their same journey, nearly a century later.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Welcoming new citizens into the Australian family is one of the best ways to celebrate Australia Day. 

New citizens like four year old Nithila, who with her parents Deepuk and Divyatharini have made a home here in Australia. 

I’m so proud of the strong, diverse and resilient country we call home.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Building more homes in every part of the country.

We've just announced new projects that'll mean 25,000 more homes across New South Wales.

And they'll be connected to the transport, services and local parks that make communities great places to live.

Because whether you live in the cities or the regions, everyone deserves the security of a roof over their head.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
New roads don’t just get you there quicker - they also create jobs, boost the economy, and support new housing.

That’s what our investment in Western Sydney is doing, with two major road upgrades.

It’s also a safeguard against floods, improving vital evacuation routes and access for emergency services in the Hawkesbury-Nepean Valley.

Because we want to make sure our suburbs thrive as we keep building Australia's future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
My uni classroom definitely didn’t look like this.

This facility at the University of Newcastle does more than teach students. It helps develop the technology of the future. 

Australia’s always been at the forefront of innovation: from wifi to the cochlear implant.  

We’re backing this facility with a $20 million investment to continue that legacy. 

And helping turn great Aussie inventions into jobs.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Tomorrow is Australia Day, a chance to celebrate everything we love about our country. Whether you’re heading to the beach, having friends over for a barbecue or hitting the road for the long weekend, I wish you all a safe and Happy Australia Day.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This was the scene of a hate crime. 

An act of vile, antisemitic violence. 

Every act of antisemitism is an affront to who we are as Australians. 

This was an attack targeted at the Jewish community. And it is a crime that concerns us all because it is also an attack on the nation and society we have built together. 

Child care centres are places of joy and discovery for children. 

They are a place parents trust to look after the most precious thing in their world – their children. 

The antisemitic attack here in Maroubra is as cowardly as it is disgusting. 

It is designed to add to the fear and pain the Jewish community are enduring right now. 

Yet this crime will strike at the heart of every parent, and all Australians.

It is something all of us condemn, and all of us must work together to stop.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
These centres will educate young Australians about the horrors of the Holocaust. 

They will teach them from an early age that such prejudice, hatred and violence has no place here. 

Not now, not ever.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Happy birthday Triple J.

Fifty years of opening our ears to music we would not have heard without you. 

A platform for Australian musicians, and a launch pad for broadcasters, journalists, and comedians.

Triple J, and Double J are a central part of Australian cultural life, enriching our lives and expanding our perspectives.

Thank you for 50 incredible years - wishing you another incredible half century.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The vile graffiti we’ve seen overnight, including at the Newtown Synagogue, is abhorrent and needs to stop immediately. 

Australia is a better place than this. 

We made it illegal to use Nazi and other hate symbols because there’s no place in Australia for antisemitism.

The people that committed these crimes should face the full force of the law.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re finishing the NBN and making sure it stays in public hands 🙌 

A bad internet connection impacts every day life, and Australians in regional areas, like here in the Shoalhaven, know this first hand.

With many people still stuck on copper without access have access to an upgraded fibre NBN.

That’s why we’re finishing it. Because every Australian family and business deserves access to high speed internet at an affordable price.

When we say building Australia’s future, we mean in every part of the country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
⬇️ Send this to someone who needs to know about our free Medicare Urgent Care Clinics.

They’re right across Australia. Chances are there’s one near you.

You can find your closest Urgent Care Clinic here: https://t.co/ekynvbZEX6

So next time you’ve got a cut, burn or break – you know where to go.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re building more homes for Australians.

And to do that, we need more of the vital infrastructure that connects them. 

That’s what we’re getting on with here in Hobart, so 600 new homes can be built.

We’re giving more people in this stunning part of the country the security of a roof over their head.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Anne Stanley is a champion for her community of Werriwa.

Her advocacy has helped secure a $1 billion road upgrade for 15th Avenue.

@AnneWerriwa will always fight for better roads, services and cost of living relief for the people she represents.

I’m proud to lead a team working everyday to build Australia’s future, and proud to have Anne as part of that team.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Joint statement on the ceasefire and hostage deal in the Middle East.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Congratulations @realDonaldTrump on your inauguration as 47th President of the United States. The United States is a great friend of Australia’s. Our Alliance has never been stronger. I look forward to working with you on the opportunities and challenges ahead.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Trade blockages on Aussie beef exports to China have been lifted in a win for jobs, for farmers and for the economy.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We're unlocking more housing in regional WA with a $200 million funding boost.

These regions help drive our nation's economy. 

We'll build the homes and community infrastructure they need and deserve, like community centres, local clubs, and boat ramps. 

And we’re unlocking more jobs by allowing direct imports and exports through Wyndham Port.

Building Australia's future is about more than bricks and mortar. 

It’s about creating a better life for Australians by investing in housing, education, aged care, childcare and Medicare.

And that’s what our Labor Government is delivering.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: From tax cuts for every Australian to building more houses in the regions, my answer to this questions is always the same.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We now have more women than ever before in Cabinet.

To Ministers Gallagher, Rishworth and Aly, congratulations on your new roles. 

And to Minister Wells, welcome to the Cabinet.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
From bitumen to better services, we’re building Australia’s future!

Western Sydney is one of the fastest growing regions in NSW and todays funding announcement will help the roads in the area keep up.

The upgrade will connect Liverpool and surrounding suburbs to the new airport and the world. ✈️ 

It will mean more jobs, better access to services and safer commutes for the families and workers in the area.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Finishing the rollout of high speed internet, and keeping the NBN in public hands, is part of building Australia's future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We’ll upgrade the NBN to make it faster - and make sure it stays affordable.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Because no matter where you live, Labor wants every community to thrive.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Jobs up. Emissions down.

Tomago aluminium smelter is a huge job creator – and uses a lot of energy.

Today we’ve announced support as they switch to cheap, reliable renewable energy. 

Making more things in Australia, using Australian resources - and acting on climate change.

We’re building Australia’s future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Lake Nash Cattle Station near Alpurrurulam in the NT is one of the farms benefitting.

Aussie beef is the best in the world – and it’s now back on the menu internationally thanks to the determined efforts of this government.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
All you need is your Medicare card at our Urgent Care Clinics. 

We’ve opened 87 of them across the country, including this one in Perth. 

They’re for when it’s urgent but not an emergency.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: The 2025 Young Australian of the Year, Dr. Katrina Wruck is a scientist and entrepreneur using green chemistry and water purification to transform industries and inspire First Nations youth in STEM.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Facilities like the Cairns PCYC are what make our communities great places to live.  

It’s where kids make friends, learn new skills, and families can come together. 

Today we’re announcing more than $50 million for housing and community infrastructure projects across Far North Queensland. 

We’re building Australia’s future right across our country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And they're free – all you need is your Medicare card. 

They're making a real difference to people's health, and they're helping with the cost of living. 

Labor will always defend Medicare.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Congratulations to @patcummins30 and the Australian cricket team on a fantastic victory in an enthralling tough series #AUSvIND 🇦🇺🇮🇳
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
All Australians are appalled by the attack in New Orleans, a shocking act of violence aimed at people celebrating the new year together. 

Our first thoughts in this moment are with the victims and their loved ones. Our nation stands with the people of the United States.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
LNP governments talk. Labor governments build. 
 
The Rocky Ring Road is an example of that. 

After a decade of inaction under the former government, work is finally underway here in Rockhampton. 

And it will happen right up and down the Bruce Highway thanks to our $7.2 billion funding injection.

It's a lifeline for the Queensland and will unlock economic growth, build flood resilience, reduce travel times, improve road safety and support jobs.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
That's what our Bruce Highway investment means to Wayne.

Wayne's been an ambo driving on the Bruce for decades, so he knows just how important road safety is.

Today I told him the good news: we're fixing this vital road, all the way from Brisbane to Cairns.

Our record $7.2 billion investment into the Bruce Highway will get Queenslanders where they need to go sooner and safer. 

And in Wayne's words: it will save lives.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: When the fifth test starts on Friday, the SCG will be a sea of pink in support of the great work of the McGrath Foundation. Go Australia!
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We're building a child care system that's affordable and accessible for every family.

We'll guarantee three days of early education and build new centres right around the country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Thousands more homes in regional Queensland.

That's what we'll deliver by investing in housing and community infrastructure – including here in Mt Isa.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re building Australia’s future – literally. 

It means building the infrastructure our growing suburbs need. 

Here in Alkimos on the outskirts of Perth, we’ve got train stations being built and new amenities going in.

And all this is happening before all the homes are built, not afterwards.  

Today construction on a new pool and recreation centre kicked off – right next to the train line. 

My government is investing in community infrastructure across the country to make our suburbs great places to live and raise a family.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Here’s to a great 2025.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Happy New Year, Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We’re making Bruce Highway safer, giving it the upgrade Queenslanders have always needed with a record $7.2 billion investment.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I know things are still tough, but with wages rising and inflation going down, we're heading into 2025 with determination and optimism.

Because working together we can build a stronger Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I will always invest in the Australian people.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Labor policies that have kicked-in this week:

✅ Tens of thousands of Free TAFE places, including 20,000 in construction and housing.

✅ It is now a criminal offence to deliberately underpay workers.

✅The max cost of PBS medicines is now frozen for 12 months (at our reduced Cheaper Medicines rate).

✅  We’ve stopped debit card surcharges when paying at Commonwealth agencies like the ATO.

✅ Pay rises for aged care workers kick in.
 
✅ New minimum pay rates for entry-level work.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Our Medicare Urgent Care Clinics have saved more than 1 million trips to the emergency department.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
President Jimmy Carter gave a century of noble service to the country he loved, to the cause of peace and to the lives of people in need all around the world. 

Jimmy Carter was a person of deep faith and a true humanitarian who dedicated his post-Presidential life to eradicating disease, preventing conflict, tackling poverty and campaigning for human rights.

In all this, his late wife Rosalynn was always his essential partner and his strongest supporter. 

Former President Carter rose from humble beginnings to leave a remarkable legacy. Beyond being elected to the Presidency or being awarded the Nobel Peace Prize, Jimmy Carter's legacy is best measured in lives changed, saved and uplifted. 

People living free from debilitating disease because of the work of The Carter Center. People with a safe home to call their own, thanks to all those he inspired to contribute to Habitat for Humanity. People spared the toll of conflict because of his tireless efforts as a negotiator. 

Our world is better a place for Jimmy Carter’s life and work. May he rest in eternal peace.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description: This is such deeply sad news. Our thoughts are with Jacob’s wife, family and friends.

description: Statement on the 20th Anniversary of the Boxing Day Tsunami.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The payments will help with essentials like food, clothing, medication and accommodation and we’re working with the Victorian Government to ensure that people who need help can get it quickly.

You can call the VicEmergency Hotline on 1800 226 226 to apply.

To the firefighters and first responders who have done so much to keep Australians safe over Christmas - we thank you.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Bushfires in the Grampians have hit this beautiful part of our country hard. 

We’ve seen homes and livestock lost. 

And we’ve also seen the best of the Australian spirit in action.

Neighbours helping out, firefighters and first responders protecting lives, and volunteers giving up their Christmas to support their community. 

We want to make sure people can get back on their feet quickly, so we're rolling out the Disaster Recovery Allowance.

It will help Aussies who have lost income because of the fires.

Those affected can apply via MyGov or call the Australian Government Emergency Information Line on 180 22 66.

We'll keep doing everything we can to support this incredible community. 

And we thank everyone who has worked day and night over the Christmas period to keep people safe.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Merry Christmas, Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: In every state and territory I’ve met Australians who want to build a stronger future. A future where no one is held back and no one is left behind.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
That's a wrap on 2024.

Tax cuts. Energy bill relief. Cheaper child care. Expanding bulk billing. Cheaper medicines. Cutting student debt. 

2024 has had it all.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Assistance is on the way for communities affected by the devastating bushfires in Victoria.

Emergency relief payments are now available for Victorians who live in an evacuation area.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Ashvini Ambihaipahar is Labor’s candidate for Barton.

Ash is a true Barton local. She grew up here and she knows what matters to the area.

She has spent her career advocating for her local community and Australian workers. 

And she’s ready to continue the work of helping with the cost of living, fixing Medicare, delivering secure and better paying jobs, and building Australia’s future.

I know Ash will work hard to continue the extraordinary legacy of Linda Burney in delivering for Barton and people across Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We’re helping you get a better deal at the checkout – cracking down on price gouging, fake discounts and unfair surcharges.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
My Government has worked tirelessly to rebuild Australia’s relationships in the Pacific. 

And today we take our relationship with Solomon Islands to a new level, by providing support to grow the size of the Royal Solomon Islands Police Force. 

This partnership will strengthen Solomon Islands’ domestic security and will enhance its ability to contribute to regional stability. 

It affirms Australia as Solomon Islands' security partner of choice. 

Prime Minister Manele and I make this announcement today from Honiara and Canberra.

Because we are stronger and more secure when we act together.

Under my Government, Australia will be the partner for Solomon Islands we always should have been.

biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Australians would pay more under Peter Dutton.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: If you're working today, thank you. You deserve your penalty rates.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Fifty years ago Cyclone Tracy devastated Darwin, claiming the lives of more than 60 Australians.

It destroyed homes, businesses, and the old Museum and Art Gallery of the Northern Territory.

Now, the Museum is home to the Cyclone Tracy story, with an exhibition to commemorate those we lost.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
John Marsden wanted young Australians to read more and his writing made that happen. 

Vivid, funny, quintessentially Australian, he wrote with a real love for our land and a true sense of our people’s character. 

His was a great Australian voice that spoke to all ages, here and around the world. 

John’s work will live long in our national memory.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Magnificent victory by Australia in a fantastic test match #AUSvINDIA 🏏
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
“We all found our own ways to survive that night.”

That’s what Antony told us tonight about Christmas Eve in 1974, when Cyclone Tracy hit Darwin.

As a 12 year old who’d gone to sleep dreaming of a perfect Christmas morning, Antony was forced to huddle under his house and wait out the cyclone that devastated Darwin and killed over 60 Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia and Timor-Leste are great friends with a shared vision for a stable, prosperous and secure region.

Today we’re pleased to announce new initiatives to support Timor-Leste’s economic development and deepen our bilateral ties.

You can read our joint statement below.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Horrific news from the Magdeburg Christmas market in Germany. 

My thoughts and those of all Australians are with the victims and their loved ones.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Walking amongst the exhibition today on Christmas Eve was a solemn reminder of the destruction wreaked on Darwin 50 years ago.

And a demonstration of the resilience and strength of this community in the face of unimaginable loss.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Thank you to all our extraordinary Australian Defence Force personnel serving at home and overseas this Christmas.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Australians are thinking of our friends and neighbours in Vanuatu after the devastating earthquake that struck their home this afternoon. We are closely monitoring the situation and stand ready to assist the people of Vanuatu in any way we can.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australians in need of emergency consular assistance should contact the Australian Government 24-hour Consular Emergency Centre (+61 6 261 3305 from overseas or 1300 555 135 in Australia). 

Australia stands ready to provide further assistance to our Pacific family in their time of need.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our thoughts this morning are with the two sailors that tragically lost their lives in the Sydney to Hobart race overnight. 

The Sydney to Hobart is an Australian tradition, and it is heartbreaking that two lives have been lost at what should be a time of joy.

We send our love and deepest condolences to their families, friends and loved ones.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Announcing Basem Abdo as Labor’s candidate for Calwell at the next election. 

Basem lives with his wife Natascha in Greenvale in Melbourne’s north.

He’s passionate about manufacturing, education and helping young people in the area get the best start in life. 

He loves his multicultural community, and wants Labor to keep delivering free TAFE, more jobs and more options to see the doctor. 

Basem will make an excellent representative of this beautiful part of Melbourne.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Help is on the way. 

Throughout the day, Royal Australian Air Force aircraft have been loaded with equipment and personnel headed for Vanuatu.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Matt Gregg is Labor’s candidate for Deakin at the next election. 

As a lawyer and an educator, Matt firmly believes in fairness and wants to help create a future for young people that they can feel excited about.

He’s running to unseat the current MP Michael Sukkar, who has opposed tax cuts and voted against more housing for Victorians. 

Matt will be a great representative for the people of Melbourne’s eastern suburbs, and I can’t wait to have him as part of my Labor Government.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We secured early childhood education and care workers a 15% pay rise, because what they do matters. 

They teach our children at a time when they're learning the most. 

It's such an important job. 

We're also going to build more childcare centres, and make it easier to access subsidised care. 

We're making it easier for parents, better for our young ones, and fairer for the workers – which is good for the country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Kevin Andrews dedicated his life to the things he cared for most: family, faith, community and nation. He served all four with integrity and devotion. 

Kevin's Liberal colleagues and his Labor opponents would agree, he was a man of conviction. He was respected as someone who held his views firmly and argued them fiercely. 

My condolences to his wife Margie, and to the Andrews family.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Peter Dutton’s nuclear scheme means higher bills and fewer jobs. 

We’re investing in cleaner, cheaper energy to create jobs and cut emissions.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
A massive congratulations to all the Year 12s who’ve received their final results. 

Getting here has taken so much hard work, resilience and dedication. You can be proud of everything you’ve put in.

If you’re planning on more study, we’re making it easier:

Free TAFE courses. A new prac payment. And lower repayments on student loans.

And to the parents, teachers, and school staff who have made such a difference along the way, thank you.

Here’s to a bright future ahead.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: This industry supports the local community, and it boosts our national economy.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Jess Teesdale is a local teacher here in Launceston, and I’m so pleased to announce her as Labor’s candidate for Bass at the next election. 

After studying, Jess found that she had to leave the state to find work. She wants to create an environment in Tasmania where people don’t have to leave to access good job opportunities. 

I want Jess to be a strong local voice in a government that will continue delivering Medicare Urgent Care Clinics and better services for Tasmanians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
His is a story of bravery and resilience, and he’s not alone in that.

So many people in the Darwin community showed incredible strength in the face of disaster. 

It was a privilege to hear their stories in Darwin tonight, exactly 50 years on.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Announcing Gabriel Ng for Menzies. 

Gabriel is a young dad who lives in Donvale with his kids and wife Maaya. 
 
He wants to be part of the team delivering tax cuts, cheaper child care, and more Medicare Urgent Care Clinics. 

And I’m so happy to have him on board.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The siege in Sydney’s Lindt Cafe shook a city and shocked a nation. 

Ten years on, we stop to think of those who lost their lives, and those whose lives were changed forever. 

We particularly hold on to the memory of Katrina Dawson and Tori Johnson, who never went home again. 

This morning in Martin Place, we laid down hydrangeas and sunflowers – their favourite flowers. 

Our thoughts are with their families, some of whom joined us today, and with all those whose lives were touched by this horrendous ordeal. 

We ache for all who loved them and, as we mark this saddest of anniversaries, we hold them all in our hearts.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia and Papua New Guinea are united by our love of Rugby League. 

This is why I am delighted to announce the Australian Government is supporting a PNG team to join the National Rugby League competition from 2028.

The new team will belong to the people of Papua New Guinea.  

It will call Port Moresby home. 

And I know it will have millions of proud fans barracking for it, from day one. 

Our Pacific Rugby League Partnership will also deepen Australia’s sporting connections more broadly in the Pacific. 

We are the nearest of neighbours and truest of friends. 

As Prime Minister Marape has said, Australia is Papua New Guinea’s security partner of choice.  

We are honoured to carry that responsibility and to reflect this across the length and breadth of our relationship.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I am pleased to confirm that Australian citizens, Si Yi Chen, Michael Czugaj, Matthew Norman, Scott Rush and Martin Stephens have returned to Australia this afternoon. 

I thank President Prabowo Subianto for his compassion.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We're making child care more affordable and closer to home.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Child care centres like this one in Melbourne offer kids the best start in life. 

That’s why we’re going to build 160 new centres across the country.

And we’ll scrap the activity test to guarantee that every family can afford 3 days of child care.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The workers here at Tassal in Strahan make a great product that ends up on dinner plates across Australia and around the world.

We can preserve this beautiful part of the world while supporting jobs and the wonderful people who live here.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: ICYMI: We're building 160 new child care centres across the country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Ending antisemitism requires work across governments, across police forces, and across communities. 

This new police Special Operation will focus on threats, violence, and hatred towards Australia’s Jewish community.

As confirmed by authorities today, the Adass Israel Synagogue attack will be investigated as a terrorist incident. 

It’s the third arson attack, after the attack on Josh Burns’ office and the Sydney Woollahra car incident.

In response, the Government has set up AFP Special Operation Avalite, a Commonwealth-led team that will work with state and territory police forces. 

Antisemitism has no place in Australia. 

We stand with Australia’s Jewish community.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
After the devastating earthquake in Port Vila, the people of Vanuatu have a long road to recovery ahead. 

Specialist medical and rescue crews, as well as members of the Australian Federal Police, will be on the ground from this evening.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I want the community to know that we will see this synagogue rebuilt.

And we will see those who burned it brought it justice.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The fire here at the Adass Israel Synagogue in Melbourne was beyond despicable. 

It was terrorism.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today we've announced new funding to boost security at Jewish community sites, including synagogues and schools.

Everyone has the right to be proud of who they are and to feel welcome, safe and supported in Australia.

Antisemitism has no place in our country. We unequivocally condemn it.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The incident in Sydney is an outrage and another antisemitic attack. 

I will be briefed by AFP Operation Avalite officials this morning.

I stand with the Jewish community and unequivocally condemn this attack.

There is no place for hatred or antisemitism in our community.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Mark Dreyfus
description: I want to thank our brave police officers and first responders for your courageous efforts. The AFP will continue to support NSW Police as needed.
biography: Authorised by Mark Dreyfus KC MP, ALP, Mordialloc. Federal Attorney-General. Member for Isaacs.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
All aboard the new METRONET Ellenbrook Line, Perth’s biggest railway expansion in 16 years.

Projects like this mean less time spent in traffic and more time with family and friends. They create jobs and open up opportunities.

We’ve now completed almost 200 infrastructure projects across Australia since we were elected.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: This is another important moment in Australia's efforts to advance our partnerships with our Pacific neighbours, and to build a stronger and more secure region for every member of the Pacific family.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
AND we’ll guarantee 3 days of child care for families who need it.

Yep - we’re on the road to universal child care.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I support salmon farming on Macquarie Harbour because it means jobs for Tasmania.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re lowering costs and expanding Medicare.

Peter Dutton wants to cut and gut your healthcare.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I came here today with Josh Burns to make it clear that all Australians stand with this community in this deeply distressing time.

This wonderful part of Melbourne is a tribute to the extraordinary contribution that the Jewish community have made to our country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia benefits from a peaceful, secure and prosperous region. 

And the Nauru-Australia Treaty that I signed with President Adeang today meets the needs of both of our countries. 

It keeps Nauru’s people connected to the world and financially secure, and it keeps our region safe.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: What’s on your Spotify Wrapped?
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Paying with a debit card shouldn't cost you more.

So we're cracking down on unfair card surcharges and getting you a better deal at the checkout.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And it will now officially become law. 

We're doing everything we can to keep our kids safe.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The Sydney Jewish Museum tells us stories we must never forget. 

It speaks to the courage and resilience that the Jewish community have shown in the face of antisemitism over generations.

I heard the stories of Holocaust survivors Ernie, Mark and Ego today, along with Tanya Plibersek and Allegra Spender. 

We announced a $8.5 million upgrade that will ensure the museum can teach more Australians, especially students. 

I want young people to know this history – and to know that prejudice, hatred and violence has no place in Australia’s present or its future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: JUST PASSED: Our bill to help you buy a home with as little as a 2% deposit.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Big challenge ahead for the PM’s XI at Manuka Oval this week against an amazing Indian side. 



But as I said to PM @narendramodi, I’m backing the Aussies to get the job done.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Medicare Urgent Care Clinics like this one in Maroubra are taking the pressure off busy hospital emergency departments. 

Nearly half the patients say they would have gone to the local emergency department if their Medicare Urgent Care Clinic was not there. 

I’m proud our Labor Government has delivered 84 of these clinics across Australia, with more on the way.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We've just released our response to the Royal Commission into Defence and Veteran Suicide.

We’ve lost too many lives. Every single one is heartbreaking. 

We must do better. 

We’ll make the most comprehensive reforms ever to prevent suicide and improve the mental health of serving personnel and veterans.

We’ll take important action on more than 104 recommendations, including:

- Establishing a new agency focused on mental health & wellbeing.
- Setting up a new, independent body to oversee the reform.
- Ensuring serving members get the support they deserve when they transition to life outside the Defence Force.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: They deserve more than our thanks, they deserve this pay rise.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Throughout this year, we've been working hard to deliver cost of living relief. There's more to do, and we'll work every day to deliver for Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The PM’s XI and Indian cricket teams are keen to get out on the field.

The rain has delayed play for today, but it’s been great to chat with players and fans at Manuka Oval.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia is proud to be home to a large and thriving Australian-Czech community.  

I was pleased to discuss their part in our national story with President Petr Pavel of the Czech Republic today. 

We also spoke about our growing relationship and shared actions on global challenges, including support for Ukraine.

Welcome to Australia, @prezidentpavel 🇦🇺🇨🇿
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We helped Codie buy a home, and you could be next. 

With our First Home Guarantee, she bought a place down the road from where she grew up – and only needed a 5% deposit.

We've now passed Help to Buy, another way you can get into your own place with a deposit as low as 2%.
 
If you've worked hard and done all the right things but still can't get a deposit together, this could make all the difference.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: PASSED: Our bill to wipe $3 billion in student debt for more than 3 million Aussies.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Astrophysicist. Ornithorhynchus. Filibuster. 

These are some of the words this year’s Prime Minister’s Spelling Bee winners tested me on. 

Pretty impressive for children aged 9, 10 and 13! 

Congratulations to Echo, Jillian and Aditya on your very impressive spelling skills.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Don't tell Toto!
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Domestic, family, and sexual violence goes against everything we hold dear as Australians. On the International Day for the Elimination of Violence against Women, we honour the memories of those whose lives and futures were stolen. 

Together, we can work to break the cycle. We must listen and learn from those who have lived it. And we must give support and care to those who need it.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
What do electric vehicles, wind turbines and mobile phones have in common? They’re all made with critical minerals.

So we’re helping fund a new refinery to produce more of them right here in Western Australia.

Creating jobs. Boosting the economy. Building Australia’s future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: If you’ve got a student debt, it’s about to get smaller.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
These texts aren’t just annoying, they cost Australians millions of dollars a year.

We’re cracking down, requiring telcos to block texts pretending to be from trusted companies.

Making sure you don’t have to second guess every text - and keeping you protected.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our veterans have done so much for us, and they have so much to offer. 

As they transition to the civilian world, our service members bring with them the values of service, courage, integrity, respect and excellence. 

The Prime Minister’s Veteran Employment Awards are a chance to recognise the role they play, along with their employers and partners. 

They stepped up for Australia, and now they’re finding new ways to lift up the nation. 
 
A huge congratulation to tonight’s winners and nominees.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Stabilising Australia’s relationship with China is in the interests of both our countries. 

Dialogue is critical, and we’ve made encouraging progress.

Trade is flowing more freely. 

And that brings benefits to both countries, and to people and businesses on both sides. 

Our approach will remain patient, calibrated and deliberate. 

It is important that we have direct discussions on the issues that matter to us, and to the stability and prosperity of our region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: When it comes to protecting our kids we have to do more than wring our hands. We need to take action.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: More trade means more jobs. That’s what I’m promoting here at APEC and next week at the G20.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our government has backed workers from day one. 

We’ve supported pay rises for Australia’s lowest paid workers. We’ve ensured that same job, same pay is the law of the land. And over one million jobs have been created since we came to government.

Our plan to get wages moving again is working, and this month we’ve seen Australian workers paid an historic amount. 

We know people are under pressure, and we’ll keep working every day to deliver the security and cost of living help they need.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I’ve got a message for mums and dads: we are on your side. We’ve got your back.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our 🇦🇺🇮🇳 renewable energy partnership is officially launched. 

Great to see India’s Prime Minister @narendramodi today on the sidelines of the G20 Summit in Brazil. 

This new partnership will boost two way investment in the renewable energy sectors in things like solar, green hydrogen and the renewables workforce.  

We are doing so much work together on driving renewable energy transition to meet our net zero targets.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today we honoured a great Australian with a great Australian tradition - Sunday arvo footy. 

Jack Fitzgibbon served his community in so many ways, none more important than serving his country in the Australian Defence Force. 

His passing is a reminder that there are no easy days for those who defend our nation.

I am honoured to stand with his father and my friend Joel Fitzgibbon as we remember him today at the Jack Fitzgibbon Cup.

The Cup supports the important work of the Commando Welfare Trust, providing support to Special Forces soldiers, veterans and family members where the system cannot.

Thank you to all of the incredible Australians who serve and put themselves on the line for all of us.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: TODAY: We're introducing our bill to make 16 years the minimum age for social media.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
It’s a privilege to join the community of St Nicholas Antiochian Orthodox Church to celebrate the Feast Day of St Nicholas tonight.

St Nicholas is a powerful example of kindness, charity and humanity, and this church so wonderfully embodies these ideals.

Here we see the strength of faith, and the connection of community. A community that holds its door open in welcome.

I wish all those who celebrate a blessed Feast Day of St Nicholas.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Great to meet kids living with type-1 diabetes, who have come to Parliament with the Juvenile Diabetes Research Foundation. 

We're proud to support their work in helping children reach their full potential.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Here at this summit in Brazil, I’ve been able to meet with leaders to work on solutions to our shared challenges. 

Addressing supply chain issues that have pushed up prices, global action on climate change, and the opportunities that clean energy provides to our economies were key points of discussion.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Congratulations to President Surangel Whipps Jr on a second term as President of the Republic of Palau.

We look forward to continuing to work as friends and partners to ensure a peaceful, stable and prosperous Pacific.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Our plan for cheap renewable energy is good policy.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: The Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation forum is where our region’s economic leaders work on our shared challenges.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Working together we can deliver a better, more prosperous and more secure future for Australians and Brits alike. 🇦🇺🇬🇧
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: That's not all - a re-elected Labor Government will wipe another 20% off everyone’s HECS debt and lower repayment thresholds so there’s less coming out of your pocket every week.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today I met with Prabowo Subianto for the first time since his inauguration as President of Indonesia.

I thanked @prabowo for his leadership to finalise our bilateral Defence Cooperation Agreement.

Australia and Indonesia are near neighbours and close partners. 🇦🇺🇮🇩

And I look forward to working with President Prabowo on the shared challenges facing our region and our peoples.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The outcomes achieved here at the G20 are all about creating jobs in Australia. 

Inflation is a global problem, and it requires a global response. 

And Australia’s relationships around the world matter.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Peru is hosting APEC at an important time as the world faces an inflation challenge. 
 
@presidenciaperu Boluarte and I spoke about the upcoming summit, the Australia-Peru relationship, and our growing commercial ties.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Anne Urquhart has been a champion for North West Tasmania as a Senator. 

She’s helped deliver tax cuts for every taxpayer here, more than 600,000 cheaper scripts, an Urgent Care Clinic in Devonport and more.

As Labor’s candidate for Braddon, Anne will continue her important work to help with the cost of living and build for Tasmania’s future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We're making 16 years old the minimum age for social media. Here's why.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Whether it’s inflation, trade, or climate change, it’s more important than ever that Australia has a seat at the table to address global issues that directly affect Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
What happens in the world matters to Australia. 

My focus here at APEC will be on promoting economic and trade opportunities that support our interests, and promote jobs. 

It comes at an important time as we work through the global inflation challenge. 

APEC world leaders will come together over the coming days with a determination to promote the economic growth and business links that boost wages and prosperity.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Rebecca White fights for what she believes in.

And she believes in this community. 

She’s represented this area for fourteen years in the Tasmanian Parliament - and now she's determined to bring their voices to Canberra. 

Whether it’s cutting debt for students, delivering tax cuts, or building the infrastructure Tasmanians need, she’ll work hard for her community every day.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our growing relationship with India matters to Australia. 

Great to meet with External Affairs Minister @DrSJaishankar today in Canberra. 🇦🇺🇮🇳
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: This one’s for all the TAFE students out there.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Met with Australia's special envoy to combat antisemitism Jillian Segal this morning in Canberra to talk about the work we're doing to make Jewish Australians feel safe.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
At the going down of the sun and in the morning. We will remember them. 

Lest We Forget.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Sports clubs keep our communities running.

Providing a space for young and old to be social and stay active, all while boosting our economy. 

Not to mention getting kids onto sport fields and off screens.

Great to be with @PeterKhalilMP to talk to local sport clubs in Melbourne.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Australia and Japan work together to support peace, security and prosperity in the Indo-Pacific. Congratulations to @shigeruishiba on your re-appointment, I look forward to strengthening our special strategic partnership.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
