Because of our changes, thousands of workers are earning up to $30,000 more per year. 

Labor will always stand for a fair go for Aussie workers.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our economic plan has prioritised helping people under pressure while fighting inflation.  

Because of our work, inflation today is less than half of what we inherited from the former government.

There’s more to do, and we will continue to provide support.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Being part of the conversation means Australia gets to shape the solutions to create more opportunities for our businesses and our people to thrive.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I know parents are worried about the impacts of social media on their children.

That’s why we're implementing a minimum age of 16. It will help protect kids and give parents peace of mind.

Great to chat about it with Craig this morning on ABC Sydney.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Democracy is the backbone of our Parliaments. 

A strength demonstrated in the tremendous diversity and mobilising power of the nations represented at the Commonwealth Parliamentary Conference tonight. 

But democracy is more than abstract - it’s about making a positive difference, delivering for people, taking on the big challenges.

Challenges like tackling climate change and seizing the economic opportunities of clean energy.

Challenges we will take on together.

Thank you for the contribution you make to life and strength of Parliaments around the world.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Statement on Remembrance Day 2024.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Emma McKeon retires today as one of Australia's all-time sporting greats. Young Australian of the Year, our most decorated Olympian, and admired across the nation for her tenacity, grace and humility. 

Emma is a champion in every sense of the word, and a role model so many will look up to for generations to come. All Australians wish her all the very best for the future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
TAFE changes lives. 

And in the past two years, over half a million Australians have enrolled in fee-free TAFE thanks to our government. 

A strong TAFE sector means more tradies, more carers, and more workers who will drive our digital transformation. 

It's why we'll make free TAFE permanent, nationwide. 

I spoke to business leaders at the Australian Chamber of Commerce and Industry about the vital role that our investments in TAFE and university play in creating opportunities for individuals, and for driving growth and productivity in our economy.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Congratulations to President Donald Trump on his election victory.
 
Australians and Americans are great friends and true allies.
 
Working together, we can ensure the partnership between our nations and peoples remains strong into the future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Summits like the G20 are all about how we can make sure that everyone benefits from economic growth. 

By making Australia’s voice heard, we can shape solutions that benefit Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The Kmart Wishing Tree helps make Christmas a little bit brighter for so many families in need. 

I'm proud it has support from across the Parliament. A huge thanks to all the Salvation Army volunteers, and to all those donating presents to this worthy cause.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: A minimum age for social media of 16 years will make a difference.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And we'll reduce the amount you have to repay each year. 

The Liberals and Nationals oppose cutting debt, and would leave millions of Australians worse off.

But we know it's the right thing to do, because it'll widen the doors of opportunity for more young Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Whether you study at uni or TAFE, Labor will always have your back.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Strengthening Medicare is at the heart of our agenda. And these heroes are at the heart of Medicare. 

Tonight we celebrated our incredible health care workers at the Stronger Medicare Awards in Parliament House.

Their passion for their patients and dedication to their communities changes lives.

Thank you for all you do.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Hear it here first: a re-elected Labor Government will wipe 20% off your student debt.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Cutting student debt and making free TAFE permanent.

We're doing both, because both are essential for building Australia’s future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: As long as there's a Labor Government, free TAFE is here to stay.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Study something you love and get a great job, all for free.

We're locking in free TAFE to give you that opportunity – permanently.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Happy Bandi Chhor Divas! 

Wonderful to celebrate at Gurdwara Sahib Glenwood today and open the newly expanded kitchen, serving thousands of people every week.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This is big news for our move to renewable energy.

Mars Petcare is powering their pet food production with a new renewable energy project.

Feeding Aussie pets with the first large-scale food manufacturing site to deliver a 100% renewable steam solution.  

But pet food is just the beginning. Projects like these can power manufacturing and industry across the board, processing products like paper, wood, textiles and metals. 

Another example of what we can achieve when business and government work together.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re working on the inflation challenge from every possible angle, and our efforts are making a difference. 

Today’s inflation data reveals a 2.8% annual rate. It’s the lowest figure since 2021, and it’s less than half of what we inherited when we came to government. 

We know inflation has put Australians under a lot of pressure.

And we'll keep working on ways to deliver more cost of living relief while keeping inflation in check.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Gold medal skills on display from the students at NSW TAFE's Hunter campus. 

We've invested in the Net Zero Manufacturing Centre of Excellence here because jobs and clean energy go hand in hand. 

Skilling up the clean energy workforce that will power Australia.

We know that renewable energy means cheaper power bills.

And while the Liberals and Nationals are pushing for their nuclear scheme that costs too much and takes too long, we’re backing the clean energy workforce with jobs now.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Tell a friend: student loan repayments will be lower next year under Labor.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Deepavali celebrates the victory of light over darkness. 

Fantastic to join with the Tamil Australian community at the Sydney Murugan Temple today. 

The temple draws in people from all walks of life every day, and has become a sanctuary for Western Sydney's South Asian Hindu community.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Good to speak this morning with President Trump to personally congratulate him on his election victory. 

We talked about the importance of the Alliance, and the strength of the Australia-US relationship in security, AUKUS, trade and investment.   

I look forward to working together in the interests of both our countries.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: That's why we made child care cheaper, saving families thousands of dollars a year on fees.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Satapuala Village in Samoa is decked out in green and gold.

It was such an honour to receive the chiefly title of Toeolesulusulu from the village. A sign of deep respect between our people.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today I spoke with His Holiness Mar Awa III, Catholicos-Patriarch of the Assyrian Church of the East who is visiting Australia with an international delegation of his bishops. 

Assyrian-Australians have long been part of our thriving multicultural society, and have made our country a better place.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Deepening our co-operation on economic growth, climate and security. 🇦🇺🇬🇧 

Moving to renewable energy is an opportunity for new industries and new jobs in both our countries. 

Today, we’ve announced more actions to power up our collaboration on climate and energy.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Over the last few days I’ve been working with Commonwealth leaders for the common good.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today we honour an Australian hero, the late Private Richard Norden, with the Victoria Cross for Australia. 

For most conspicuous acts of gallantry in action in the presence of the enemy in the 'AO Surfers' Area of Operations in the Bien Hoa province, Vietnam, on 14 May 1968, during the Battle of Fire Support Base Coral.

Richard Norden’s courage under fire and his disregard for his own safety make him a more than worthy recipient. 

His citation tells of his extraordinary courage, advancing under heavy fire to save the lives of his friends.

Today, in honouring Richard Norden and all he fought for, Australia also honours all those who fought for him. 

His fellow veterans, those who served alongside him and those who took up his cause when they learned his story. 

Everyone who kept alive the memory of his valour.

Everyone who has championed and advocated due recognition of Richard Norden.

And everyone who has kept faith with Australia’s promise to remember all those who have served and their loved ones. 

Lest We Forget.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Wishing a happy Festival of Lights to all those celebrating over the coming days.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: At the next election, the biggest threat to better pay for workers will come from Peter Dutton and the Liberals and Nationals, who want to undo this law.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Same Job, Same Pay is now the law of the land.

Tonight I met with Danielle and other Mining and Energy Union workers in Brisbane to say this: we will always support a fair go for Aussie workers. 

Danielle was doing the same job as her colleagues, with the same skills, but getting $33,000 less per year because she was employed through a labour hire business. 

It was unfair, and we fixed it.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Celebrating our beautiful multicultural Australia today at Sydney’s Norton Street Italian Festa. 🇦🇺🇮🇹
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: An important one.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We spoke with locals who are excited for the new residents to join the neighbourhood.

Getting more homes built means more roofs over the heads of Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: It will provide a home to around 130 people when complete, and during construction apprentices from The King’s Trust are being employed.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: ICYMI: Student loans will be fairer next year under Labor.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: A warm welcome to King Charles today from school students, members of our Defence Force, and distinguished Australians from across our nation in his first visit as sovereign.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Congratulations President @prabowo on the occasion of your inauguration. I value our friendship and look forward to continuing to strengthen the partnership between our nations. 🇦🇺🇮🇩
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Around a third of the world’s population will be represented here over the next few days. 

Commonwealth leaders are meeting in Samoa to address the issues facing our nations, including climate change. 

And for the first time, this meeting is being hosted by a Pacific Island nation - right in Australia’s region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Thanks Brian, Xavier, Alison and everyone calling in and donating today. It was wonderful to say hi.

The money raised this weekend is going to change the lives of children and families in need.

The Telethon is largest fundraiser per capita in the world. That's something WA can be incredibly proud of.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Thrilled to be on one of my favourite shows 🎶. 

Had a great time with Adam, Myf and Alan. Tune-in tonight at 7:30 on @ABCTV
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: In case you missed it: we’re cracking down on unfair card surcharges.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
No one knows that better than the incredible workers who make up the health and care sector. 

It was a privilege to celebrate those workers with the HSU tonight. 

We’ll keep working to strengthen Medicare and back the workers who power our healthcare.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Major events shouldn't come with major fees. 

Like paying to print your own ticket, or sneaky handling and service fees that pop up at checkout.

We're tackling the unfair fees that rip Australians off.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australian lobsters rock! 🦞

Restoring trade with China is about more than sharing our incredible produce with the world. 

It’s about backing Australian small businesses like the Geraldton Fishermen’s Co-Op, and saving thousands of jobs across the country.

That’s what my government is about, and that’s what we’ve been working hard to achieve.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The security of the Pacific matters to Australia. 

That’s why we’re investing in the Pacific Policing Initiative, to help respond to emergencies and assist with major events. 

Police officers from many Pacific countries are working to support the Commonwealth Heads of Government meeting, including some trained in Brisbane.  

Two months since Pacific leaders backed this initiative, its first deployment is seeing success in Samoa.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Wonderful to see progress on this housing project today in Sydney along with His Majesty King Charles, NSW Premier Chris Minns and Housing Minister Rose Jackson.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Hamas leader Yahya Sinwar was a terrorist and the architect of the atrocities committed on October 7. 

He was an enemy of the Israeli people and an enemy of peace-loving people everywhere. His death is a significant moment and can be a vital turning point in this devastating conflict. 

Australia joins with the international community in renewing our call for the return of the hostages, urgent humanitarian support for civilians in Gaza and a ceasefire that will break the cycle of violence and put the region on the path to an enduring two state solution.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
A warm welcome back to Australia.  

Their Majesties have a deep regard for Australia, and this visit will be an opportunity to showcase the very best of our modern and dynamic nation.

Over the next few days, King Charles and Queen Camilla will meet with Australians at events in Sydney and Canberra.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Trade creates jobs for our people and helps build a future made in Australia. 

Nearly half a million jobs in Australia are linked to trade with ASEAN, and the Australian Government is boosting our two-way trade and investment. 

Here in Laos, we’re working with Australian business leaders to forge deeper links in the region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I’m honoured to be joined in Canberra today by the King of Bhutan, His Majesty Jigme Khesar Namgyel Wangchuck.

Welcome to Australia 🇦🇺🇧🇹
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Sydney really turning on the weather for Their Majesties King Charles and Queen Camilla on the final day of their Australian tour 🇦🇺
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
1 million new jobs have been created since we came to Government. 

With our pay rises for award wage workers, people are earning more. 

Our tax cuts are helping every taxpayer keep more of what they earn. 

And we're cracking down on dodgy supermarket discounts and hidden fees, so no Australian pays more than they should. 

Getting wages up. Getting costs down. Getting inflation back where it should be. Tackling the cost of living everywhere we can.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The Labor Party is powered by people. 

Thanks to all the volunteers on the phones and out and about in Queensland, fighting to deliver a @StevenJMiles government that’s doing what matters for Queenslanders.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Congratulations @ABarrMLA and @ACTLabor.

Looking forward to continuing our work for fairness, progress and opportunity for all.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
In the next five years, the economies of Southeast Asia will account for 10 per cent of global growth.  

When Australian businesses thrive here, the benefits come home - new jobs, new ideas, new technology and markets for our products.

And when Australia invests in Southeast Asia, Southeast Asia grows and gains too.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
George Negus was a giant of Australian journalism. His courage, curiosity and integrity gave millions of Australians a sense of the big issues on 60 Minutes, and a window to the world through Foreign Correspondent. 

George sought and served the truth with steely determination and a twinkle in his eye, and along the way, he made even the smallest TV screen feel that much bigger. 

He was a wonderful human being and his loss will be deeply felt by so many Australians. 

We offer his family the heartfelt condolences of our nation. May he rest in peace.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Busy two days of summits in Laos working to deliver jobs and opportunities in Australia, and to promote security in our region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Twenty-two years since the Bali bombings, we pause once more as a nation to reflect and remember.

In that place where Indonesians have for so long welcomed Australians and others from around the world, the terrorists struck at the joy of a free people. They struck at the friendship between us, without mercy, without pity.

We think of everyone - Australian, Indonesian and others from across the world —who never saw home again. We think of everyone who still carries the loss, emotional and physical.

Over the years grief does not fade. So many hearts are still tethered to that cruel night, every beat tempered by an abiding sorrow.

Amid that terrible darkness, the terrorists could not break the spirit of humanity.

Horror was met with heroism and compassion among friends and strangers alike. We refused to let terrorists drive us apart. 

We hold on to that just as we hold on to everyone Bali touched. We hold them in our hearts, never to fade.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We'll keep the NBN in public hands so good internet access is always affordable.

Whether it’s working remotely, running a business or studying at home, high speed broadband is a non-negotiable these days. 

So we’re making sure it stays in the hands of the Australian people.

Because you deserve affordable and high speed services no matter your postcode.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I thank @AlboMP and the people of Australia for today’s announcement of essential defence assistance for Ukraine totaling $170,6 million.

I am especially grateful for Australia’s brave decision to provide 49 M1A1 Abrams tanks for our defense against Russian aggression.
 
We
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Working together on climate action and building upon our shared values of democracy, human rights and the rule of law.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Radio has kept Australians connected and informed for over a century.

In times of crisis bringing us critical information.

And in our everyday lives bringing us entertainment and joy.

Today was a special broadcast to celebrate the centenary of ABC Radio in Melbourne.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
It’s game day! 🏉 Good luck to Damien Cook and the team in PNG for the PM’s XIII match 🇦🇺🇵🇬

Looking forward to a great game in celebration of a great friendship.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Sneaky fees just aren’t fair.

You shouldn’t be paying to download a ticket you’ve already purchased. And it shouldn’t be so hard to cancel a subscription.

Those are just some of the dodgy practices we’re cracking down on.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The next two days of regional meetings in Laos are important for taking forward Australia’s interests in the Indo-Pacific.

Regional stability, peace, and future prosperity cannot be taken for granted – we need to work for them, and that means working with our partners. 
 
I’ll be meeting with southeast Asian and other Indo-Pacific country leaders to press forward with our plans to deepen economic links with one of the fastest growing regions in the world.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: What happens in our region matters to Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Prime Minister Fiame, thank you for hosting Commonwealth leaders this week, and for your leadership on climate change.

I look forward to continuing to work together in the interests of our nations and people. 🇦🇺🇼🇸
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Ever found more air than chips in your chip packet?

More air, less product, same price. It's called shrinkflation, and it's ripping Australians off.

We’re fixing it, making sure you get good value at the checkout with stronger unit pricing and big penalties for supermarkets doing the wrong thing.

There’s more to do, so we’ll keep working to get you a fair deal at the checkout.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our Greek Australian community is such a vibrant part of our multicultural nation.

I’ve seen that in my home of Marrickville, and in so many local businesses, sport groups, and community organisations across Australia. 

Today we’re investing in the restoration of this historic Cathedral in Redfern, helping to build a new Great Hall, Library and Museum.

An investment that will benefit and serve the whole community.

And it was so special to be joined by His All-Holiness Ecumenical Patriarch Bartholomew for the occasion. 

Welcome to Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
You're not imagining it. Companies really are shrinking products to charge you more for less.

So here's what we'll do.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re cracking down on unfair and excessive debit card surcharges.

Whether you’re paying by cash or card if you’re using your own money it shouldn’t cost you more.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: As leaders of Australia, Canada and New Zealand, we met today to reaffirm our shared values and commitment to work together on international trade, the rule of law, climate change action and international peace and security.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australians deserve access to affordable, publicly owned internet.

That’s why we’re making sure the NBN stays in the hands of the Australian people.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re cracking down on the unfair prices and sneaky charges that rip Australians off.
 
It’s not fair. And it’s not on.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Former Liberal Premier Peter Gutwein is on a mission. 

He’s walking to celebrate the role migrants have played in Australia’s story, and in Australia’s future. 

“It’s important that both sides of politics reaffirm their commitment to multiculturalism,” says Peter. 

And my government is committed to a vibrant and thriving multicultural Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Congratulations Professor @matthewbailes, winner of the 2024 Prime Minister’s Prize for Science, and to all recipients for their exceptional contributions in science and teaching.

Professor Andrew Wilks, and Dr Chris Burns winners of the PM’s Prize for Innovation. And Daniel Edwards and Alice Leung for winning the PM’s Prizes for Excellence in Science Teaching.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Tu Le has spent her career helping people doing it tough in Sydney's south-west.

As the daughter of Vietnamese refugees, Tu now works as a community lawyer, standing up for exploited migrant workers.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Great to speak with @shigeruishiba to congratulate him on his election as Prime Minister of Japan. 

I look forward to working together to strengthen our strategic and economic ties and to promote a peaceful, stable and prosperous region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Australians deserve better than being ripped-off when they’re just trying to get by.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Police officers put their lives on the line to protect their fellow Australians.

Today we remember the officers who have tragically died in the line of duty.

With honour, they served. With gratitude, we remember them.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We know families are under pressure.

And they expect better from the big supermarkets than the fake discounts the ACCC have alleged. 

It’s about trust. 

That’s why we’re beefing up the ACCC with more funding to crack down on this sort of behaviour and make sure people get a fair deal.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Australia joins with global partners in calling for an immediate ceasefire across Lebanon-Israel border.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Another important meeting with Premier Li as we continue stabilising Australia’s relationship with China.

My government has worked for the removal of trade impediments and I am pleased to announce that Premier Li and I agreed to a timetable to resume full lobster trade by the end of the year, in time for Chinese New Year. 🦞
 
With our patient, calibrated, and deliberate approach, we have restored Australian trade with our largest export market. 
 
Having dialogue helps us navigate our differences and build upon areas where we can cooperate – without compromising on any Australian interests.

I also spoke to Premier Li about the full range of regional and international security issues.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I’ve worked to protect local breweries for years, reforming excise tax and ending the discrimination against small brewers of craft beer.

Because local business is so important to a thriving community and economy.

Back in my hometown to celebrate the Inner West Ale Trail tonight.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia condemns Iran’s missile attack on Israel. 

This is an extremely dangerous escalation - Australia and the global community have been clear in our calls for de-escalation. 

Further hostilities put civilians at risk.

We are monitoring the situation closely and encourage Australians in Israel to follow the advice of local authorities.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Today we are announcing a crackdown on dodgy supermarket practices.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This is going to change lives.

We've made the biggest increase in Commonwealth funding on offer to public schools across Australia. 

I want to make sure that every student in Australia, no matter where they live and learn, receives every opportunity.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Together, we will deliver more help with the cost of living for locals here in Melbourne’s west and across Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Sporting clubs are at the heart of communities across Australia.

We're proud to back them.

Great to have a hit with some rising hot shots at Epping Tennis Club.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The ACCC has made serious allegations about fake discounts on hundreds of everyday products being sold at the big supermarkets. 

It’s not right.

That’s why we’re taking action and doing everything we can to get you a fair deal at the checkout.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We made child care cheaper to give kids the best start in life and to help family budgets.

Jo Briskey has worked to make child care more accessible, and to support the early educators who make it all possible. 

She's focused on what matters for Australian families. I'm proud to have her on my team.

New data shows families are saving thousands thanks to our cheaper child care plan.

There's more to do. And with fantastic candidates like Jo, we'll get it done.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia is always better off when we work closely with our friends and partners.

A strong Quad means a stronger Australia.

Together, driven by a common ambition to ensure a free, prosperous and secure Indo-Pacific region, we’re able to face the challenges of our region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: A quick update on our work to bring down inflation and deliver cost of living relief.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today the ACCC announced it would take action on misleading prices at the supermarket. 

And this year we’ll introduce legislation for a new mandatory Food and Grocery Code. It will mean supermarkets face multi-million dollar penalties for serious breaches.

Because we want to make sure Australian consumers get a fair go.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Without our migrant communities, Australia would be so much the poorer.

And it’s important that we work together on social inclusion and cohesion.

Though we’ve come from all corners of the world, we are bound by our national values of fairness, compassion and respect.

In the long journey of our nation's story, it's not where we've come from that makes us Australian, it's where we are going. Together.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Tu knows tackling the cost of living is what matters to Australians. Living in Mount Pritchard, she'll be a strong local voice for Fowler.

We've got a free Medicare Urgent Care Clinic up and running here, we're rolling out energy bill relief to every household, and we've given every taxpayer a tax cut.

With Tu Le on our team, we'll keep helping Australians with the cost of living.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Labor governments build. 

We're working with governments across Australia to deliver infrastructure projects to make our suburbs a better place to live.

This project in Perth will remove six level crossings, create thousands of jobs, and get people home sooner and safer.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’ve delivered two budget surpluses while rolling out tax cuts for every taxpayer, energy bill relief, cheaper child care, cheaper medicines and more. 

We're fighting inflation, managing the economy responsibly - while helping Australians with the cost of living.

The Liberals never delivered a surplus in nine years, and inflation went up. 

We'll keep working to help Australians doing it tough.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: New data out today shows Labor's cheaper child care plan is saving families thousands on fees.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Defeating cancer is something we all must work together to achieve.

So today we’re announcing a comprehensive plan to eliminate cervical cancer in the Indo-Pacific, the Cancer Moonshot initiative, with our partners in the Quad. 

Because in our nations, as in every part of the world - cancer casts its shadow on the lives of our citizens and our loved ones.

Australia has led the way in developing the life-saving HPV vaccine to prevent cervical cancer, and we’re on track to eliminate it at home. 

But cervical cancer continues to take the lives of too many women, with women in the Pacific dying of the disease at up to 13 times the rate of women in Australia.

It’s not good enough, and we must take action.

I thank my friends in the Quad for their partnership on this important fight.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
While others are blocking, we're busy building. 

Work is about to start on this project to deliver 490 new social and affordable homes for Cairns.

Housing changes lives, and we’re determined to get more homes built. 

Because unlike the Liberals and Greens, we know that Australians can’t wait for new housing. 

More public housing. More homes to rent. More home ownership.

We won’t stop working to make sure every Australian has the security and safety of a roof over their head.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our two nations have stood together for decades in the cause of peace, prosperity and stability.
 
Today, we continued our work towards a stronger future.

Great to see you, my friend. 🇦🇺🇺🇸
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Tasmanians shouldn’t have to cross an ocean to get the healthcare they need. 

We’ll help them get looked after close to home by establishing the Northern Heart Centre here in Launceston. 

We’ve already opened four free Urgent Care Clinics in Tassie, made more bulk billed GP appointments available, and saved locals $9.5 million on medicine. 

Saving money and saving lives.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
A lot of people are under pressure right now and that means they’re looking for value, making the extra effort to find every discount and special. 

That’s what makes this a betrayal of trust. Treating people as fools for trying to save some money.

We’re cracking down on this kind of behaviour – to make sure Australians get a fair go at the supermarket checkout.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
With our help, Codie bought a house with a 5% deposit close to where she grew up.

She's one of 120,000 Australians to move in thanks to the First Home Guarantee Scheme.

Our Help To Buy plan will help 40,000 more Australians into their own place, but the Liberals and Greens have voted to block it. 

We need to get this done, because everyone deserves a roof over their head.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
That’s what the Quad Leaders Summit is about.

Investing in our relationships to deliver jobs, opportunity and security at home and our region.

In a more connected world, working with our close friends and partners is more important than ever.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
“I’ve called Melbourne’s west my home for a decade. It’s where my husband and I are starting a family, and I want to give back.” 

Alice Jordan-Baird’s work across education, public transport and climate resilience policy has made a difference.

Now she will continue making a difference as Labor’s candidate for Gorton.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: This will make a real difference to the retirement savings of women right across Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Great to talk with Prime Minister @narendramodi today at the Quad Leaders Summit about ways to strengthen our partnership.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia and Japan are good friends 🇦🇺🇯🇵

Today Prime Minister @kishida230 and I continued our work towards a stable, prosperous and secure Indo-Pacififc region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival!
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: BREAKING: The Liberals and Greens just voted to block more help to buy a home.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
To make housing more affordable, we need to build more homes.

We're getting on with our ambitious goal of building 1.2 million new homes.

And today we've greenlit the biggest build of social and affordable homes in over a decade.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia rocks. And so do the scientists here at Geoscience Australia. 

They’re mapping key areas of Australia to help us turn our minerals into useful things like solar panels, batteries and electronics. 

I’m so proud of the work they do to keep our industries thriving. They’re helping us build a future made in Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Sound on! 

Not every day you get a welcome like this! Thanks so much to the fantastic students at Orange Grove Public School in my electorate.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our new Support At Home program will benefit up to 1.4 million older Australians. 

Giving people more choices about the kind of care they can receive and helping them maintain their independence for longer.

These historic reforms will improve the funding, viability and quality of aged care, and will protect Australians in aged care from harm.

Older Australians built this country, they deserve dignity, respect and quality care.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Not only standing with them. Giving them a 15% pay rise.

Aged care and child care workers take care of our loved ones. Proud to stand with them. https://t.co/J1COzQ1odh","photos":["https://pbs.twimg.com/media/F3zL3aJaoAAmTOF.jpg"],"videos":null}
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Announcing: Historic reforms to aged care including empowering older Australians to stay in their own home for longer.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Inflation is now at its lowest level in three years. We’re making progress but there’s more to do.

Helping Australians who are doing it tough is our top priority.

We’ll keep working to bring costs down for families and make sure you pay a fair price at the checkout.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
TAFE has been changing lives for decades. 

It’s where many of our nurses, early childhood educators, mechanics and tradies began their careers.

As we celebrate National TAFE Day, I’m so proud we’ve been able to deliver more than 500,000 places with our fee-free TAFE plan since coming to office.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
👇 That’s what we achieve when Labor Governments work together.

A positive practical difference to peoples lives.

Honoured to support my friend @ABarrMLA at the @ACTLabor campaign launch today.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’ve now helped 120,000 people into their first home through the First Home Guarantee Scheme. 

And we’re building new homes to make housing more affordable for Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Too many lives have been affected by suicide. 

Every death is a tragedy for those who are gone, and for those left behind.

MPs on all sides of politics came together for World Suicide Prevention Day.

Because we will find the answers together, with our hearts open and our hands extended.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
NSW, today’s the day to vote Labor for your local council.

Get down to the polling booth, vote Labor and grab a democracy sausage or cake to support your local school.

Shoutout to all those volunteering today.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We understand that secure jobs and fair wages depend on thriving businesses, just as we know productivity gains depend on skilled workers and safe workplaces.

We're funding and building the skills and education, infrastructure, health care and energy that brings benefits to both business and workers.

And we’re delivering the vital certainty that drives investment and job creation.

Because a stronger economy for workers and business means and a better future for all Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I want children to have a childhood and parents to have peace of mind.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our Future Made in Australia plan is all about Australian workers and Australian companies making things here.

Because good jobs and fair wages depend on successful businesses. 

Just like the governments of John Curtin and Ben Chifley after WWII, Australia has a choice today. 

We can build a future for Australia with thriving industries through measures like Free TAFE, the National Reconstruction Fund and Production Tax Credits. 

Or we could go back down the road of sending jobs offshore like the Liberals and Nationals did when they were last in government. 

The choice is clear. 

We are building up our industrial base. 

To create more jobs and more prosperity for Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Vanessa Low talks about jumping for gold🥇🇦🇺
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Parents tell me they’re worried about what age their kids should be on social media. 

We’ll introduce legislation in this term of Parliament to enforce a minimum age for social media and other digital platforms.

It's about supporting parents and keeping kids safe.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Our plan to legislate a minimum age for social media will support parents and protect children.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australians want their leaders to act now to make housing more affordable. This is too important to wait.

Yet today, the Liberals and Greens teamed up to block more help to buy a home. 

Help to Buy would mean a smaller deposit and getting first home owners in the door faster.

We won't wait around while the Liberals and Greens play politics, which is why we're rolling out our $32 billion Homes for Australia plan.

We've got an ambitious target of 1.2 million new homes, and we're getting on with building tens of thousands more social and affordable homes.

We're working with states and territories to cut red tape and speed up approvals, and we're training a huge number of tradies at fee-free TAFE to build more homes. 

We've boosted rent assistance, and we're renovating vacant properties so families can move in.

We’re stepping up to help more Australians buy a home. The Liberals and Greens are teaming up to get in the way.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Thanks for the letter, Raf. So happy to hear you've been inspired by our Paralympians.

Can't wait to see you playing for Australia in wheelchair basketball at Brisbane 2032. 

And to all our @AUSParalympics athletes, you’ve changed so many lives for the better.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Here's what's on the agenda for tomorrow's National Cabinet.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Welcome home to our @ausparalympics athletes 🎉 

You have given the next generation new Australian heroes to follow, and you have done your country proud.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our government serves all Australians. 

We are proudly pro-business and pro-worker. 

We don’t see this as a point of tension, we see it as a matter of logic.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Working together, we can make the change that is so desperately needed. We must.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And she knows what it means to represent her community’s values, having advocated for them on Council.

As part of a Labor Government in Canberra, she’ll be delivering on cost of living, healthcare and education for West Australians everyday.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: By working together, we can address the scourge of domestic violence. I sat down with Victorian Premier @JacintaAllanMP ahead of National Cabinet on Friday to discuss the way forward.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
While we're building, the Liberals and Greens are blocking. 

Our Help to Buy plan will help 40,000 Australians to buy their own  home. 

Instead of blocking it, the Liberals and Greens should pass this much needed help today.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re working together to help West Australians with the cost of living and build a stronger future for the state.

We’ve rolled out tax cuts and energy bill relief for every West Australian.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re fully funding West Australian public schools.

I want every young Australian to get the best possible start in life. This landmark agreement with the WA Government will help change the lives of students across the state.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
My friend Bill Shorten has decided not to contest the next election.

In this term, and right through his 17 years in Parliament, he has given it everything, every day. 

Only 21 people have had the extraordinary privilege of serving as Leader of Australia’s oldest political party. 

Bill took over in 2013, united the party, re-energised the Caucus and rebuilt Labor into a strong opposition and a genuine alternative government.  

Through his years as leader, no-one worked harder than Bill, no-one brought more energy, enthusiasm, ideas and ambition to advocating for a Labor Government. 

It’s a measure of Bill’s character that he channelled the disappointment of 2019 into fighting for justice for the victims of Robodebt. 

@billshortenmp has dedicated so much of his career to building and strengthening the NDIS, and he's determined to see it through.

I’ve asked Bill to remain in Cabinet until he goes because I want him to finish the vital work he is undertaking on the NDIS, to secure the best possible outcome for people with disability, their families and carers.

Bill, thank you for everything you’ve done in the service of working people.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Trish Cook has fought for her community all her life.

Working as a nurse and midwife across metro and remote WA, Trish has walked the walk when it comes to improving the lives of West Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
More than half of my team are women. Their leadership and insights make a real difference.

For too long, electing more women was painfully incremental.

30 years ago, Labor made a crucial step forward with quotas for pre-selection in winnable seats.

The Liberals and Nationals took no action at all. In 2024, two-thirds of their federal MPs are men.

We all owe the women who pushed for positive change a debt of gratitude. 

Because governments are better when they reflect the diversity of Australia. Our team is stronger for it every day.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Street Side Medics has provided medical support for people experiencing homelessness in NSW for years. 

And now they’re bringing their life-changing services to Melbourne. 

Their vans provide mobile medical services, and they do a fantastic job. 

My government proudly supports the incredible work of Dr Nour and his team of volunteers who provide care to those facing disadvantage.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: It is devastating to learn that six Israeli hostages have been killed by Hamas. Australians offer our deepest sympathies to their loved ones and all those who grieve their loss. Every innocent life matters.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
“I wouldn’t have been able to buy if it wasn’t for the government.”

That’s what Codie told me when I stopped in for a morning cuppa at her place in Sydney. 

Thanks to our help, she only needed a 5% deposit and didn’t have to pay lender’s mortgage insurance.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re training the workers who will build and maintain our AUKUS submarines.  

The Jobs for Subs program includes over 200 places for the high priority skills we need.
 
Across the country, our AUKUS submarine program is creating around 20,000 highly skilled jobs, including 3,500 here in Western Australia. 

It’s also the single biggest investment in our nation's defence capability. 

We're strengthening our national security and helping ensure the stability and prosperity of our region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
That's why we're adding Super to Paid Parental Leave.

It will help close the gap in retirement savings for women and improve their financial security.

Because no one should be penalised for taking time off work to do the most important job there is.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Education changes lives, and my government will always invest in it.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
“I go home feeling like I’ve made a difference.”

That's why Alisha's studying early childhood education at TAFE. The course being fee-free made it an easy choice.

And students like Alisha will benefit from our 15% pay rise when they graduate.

We're making studying more affordable, and making sure early childhood educators are paid fairly for the important work they do.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Great to chat to TWU delegates at Parliament today about the crucial work they’re doing to keep transport workers safe on our roads.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We’ll legislate a minimum age for social media to keep children safe.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We're boosting rent assistance by another 10%.

Our focus is doing everything we can to help Australians with the cost of living.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: As part of a Labor Government, she will bring that passion to Canberra and work hard for her community.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Cheaper child care. Better pay for workers. That's something to smile about. 

Giving our kids the best start in life means giving them the best education and care. 

And I’m proud my government could deliver our early childhood educators a 15% pay rise.

And as part of the deal we're capping fees, so parents save too. 

We're making sure that child care is good for children, good for families, and good for the country. 

Thanks to all the staff at Goodstart Mt Waverley in Melbourne for hosting @CarinaGarlandMP and me today.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And our shared vision to make more things in Australia will see WA’s resources used to create great local jobs and grow the economy.

Across governments we’re more determined than ever to keep delivering for this great state.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Jobs of the future, for our defence force of the future.

Great to stop by ABC studios in Perth this morning.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
A massive battery is being built here in Collie, Western Australia.

Just up the road, they’re producing graphite, a vital component in making batteries.

Our vision for cleaner, cheaper energy is taking shape.

And it means Australian resources creating Australian jobs.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Peter Dutton would stand in the way of the progress we're making. His nuclear reactor plan would mean waiting decades just to end up paying more on your power bills.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today is a special day, marking the entry into force of the Australia-Tuvalu Falepili Union. 

It’s a high level diplomatic agreement that brings our two countries closer than ever before.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: ANNOUNCEMENT: We’re fully funding West Australian public schools.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Silver 🥈🥈🥈 from Lakeisha Patterson in Para-Swimming, and from Jessica Gallagher and Caitlin Ward in Para-Cycling.

And Bronze 🥉🥉 in the pool from Rowan Crothers and Brenden Hall.

You’ve done Australia so proud 🇦🇺
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: My government has made it a priority to rebuild and strengthen our Pacific relationships.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
What an incredible start for Australia in the Paris Paralympics!

Congratulations to our gold medalists 🥇🥇🥇Thomas Gallagher in Para-Swimming, and Korey Boddington and Emily Petricola in Para-Cycling.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
In the first year, up to 280 Tuvaluans will have the choice to come to Australia to visit, live, work and study. 

And in the event of major natural disasters, pandemics or military aggression, Australia will be there at Tuvalu’s request.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: The suffering and destruction from this conflict must come to an end. We stand with the international community in calling for the immediate release of all hostages, the protection of civilians and a ceasefire in Gaza.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: It will mean more integrated police forces, more stable and enduring partnerships, serving the interests of Australia and our Pacific neighbours.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I want every young Australian to get the best possible start in life. This landmark agreement with the WA Government will help change the lives of students across the state.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I still get emotional when I talk about the day I met my dad. I feel so lucky I got to know him.

Happy Father’s Day to all the dads out there. Every moment you get with family is one to cherish.

Thanks for a wonderful question Bethany, and ABC for a sit down on The Assembly.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Regional communities need representatives who get them. That's Emily Mawson to a tee.

She’s a fierce advocate for more health services in the regions, and safer working conditions for all Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Great to speak to you yesterday @narendramodi, to wish you Happy Krishna Janmashtami, and to talk about all the work Australia and India are doing as partners bilaterally and regionally, including through the Quad.

biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Julie-Ann knows how to fight for everyday Queenslanders and win.

She represented workers in the courtroom and as Labor’s candidate for Moreton she could represent her community in Canberra.

Julie-Ann is ready to work for Australians every day.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Here at the Pacific Islands Forum in Tonga I’ve had the opportunity to meet face to face with Pacific leaders to work on our shared challenges.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Pacific leaders endorsed the Pacific Policing Initiative today in Tonga.

Australia will provide substantial, long-term support to ensure this initiative succeeds.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Working for Australia’s national interests at the Pacific Islands Forum.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Quick update: More Australians can now save money on their scripts.

Since I met Jeff Australians have saved $525m on prescriptions.

Today we’ve added even more medicines to the list you can get on a 60 day script.

More medicines on the list, means more savings for Australians.
