name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This Bill is about ensuring no region, no community and no worker is left behind.

That means jobs. That means cheaper energy. It means lowering our emissions. And it means creating massive opportunities for our regions, industries, and workers.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The Paralympics are on! 160 of Australia's best are in Paris, ready for their moment on the world stage.

Best of luck @AUSParalympics! The whole country is with you, we'll all be cheering for you. We know you'll do yourselves and Australia proud.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
As Pacific countries, our security interests are intertwined. 

And under this union we commit to work together on security and defence arrangements in an enduring partnership.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The incident that occurred in Engadine this morning was shocking and distressing. 

We’re thinking of all those who were injured and hoping for their quick recovery. 

Thank you to all the first responders and brave members of the public who helped at the scene.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The security, stability and prosperity of the Pacific is vital to Australia’s future, and to our own national security. 

That’s why we’re investing in a Pacific-led policing initiative to strengthen policing capability and coordination in our region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: THIS WEEK: Our bill to establish the Net Zero Economy Authority passed the Senate.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: It’ll create jobs, boost tourism in Far North Queensland, and help more people see this natural wonder of the world.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Helping Australians with the cost of living every day. That's what we're focused on.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Congratulations to everyone who was recognised at the Agrifutures Rural Women’s Awards tonight.

I’m proud to lead a government for all Australians, no matter where they live.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
There’s an incredible view of the Great Barrier Reef here, but this facility has definitely seen better days.

After Reef HQ in Townsville was underfunded by the Liberals, it closed in 2019. 

We’re saving it by building a new facility here.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Archie has traced his family tree back through generations, telling a vast history in intricate and beautiful detail.

Archie’s earlier work ‘Family Tree’ - a forerunner to ‘Kith and Kin’ - is proudly on display at the National Gallery of Australia in Canberra for all to see.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Archie Moore took his unique Australian story to the world, and brought home gold. 

His work ‘Kith and Kin’, curated by Ellie Buttrose and commissioned by Creative Australia, won the Golden Lion at the Venice Biennale this year.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Ron Coote is a Rugby League Legend and a great Australian. 

Tonight I was honoured to announce Ron Coote as the 14th Immortal, the highest accolade in the game.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This is the runway that will connect Western Sydney with the world...

and it's nearly ready for take off ✈️  

Today Western Sydney Airport announced its first international carrier - Singapore Airlines.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
6 Premierships from 9 Grand Finals for Souths and Easts, former Australian captain who brought great joy to all who watched his extraordinary talent.

Congratulations to Ron and to all the @NRL legends inducted into the Hall of Fame tonight.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
A special kind of excellence is born in Australia’s regions.

Tonight we celebrated the remarkable women at the forefront of farming innovation, community health and safety, and strengthening our climate resilience.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: A big couple of days in Townsville.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Climate change poses unique threats to small island states in the Pacific. 

And this world-first union means Australia recognises that Tuvalu’s statehood will continue, even in the face of the worst climate impacts.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: And very soon ‘Kith and Kin’ will be on display at the Tate Modern in London, before coming to QAGOMA in Brisbane.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This airport is a game changer, with more travel options to and from Sydney.

And it also means more jobs, more investment in local businesses, and more competition to help push down flight prices.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Being at the table means Australia can help shape the solutions in our national interest.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today @JElliotMP updated the Parliament on the work we’re doing to end family and domestic violence. 

This is a priority for my Government and it will change lives.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Beautiful morning here in Townsville. So Triple M set up outside - and pulled up in listener Jodie's driveway on her birthday!

Happy birthday Jodie, and thanks for hosting me and the Triple M crew.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description: Here’s where to find them:
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
On Vietnam Veterans Day, we pay tribute to the more than 60,000 Australians who served in our uniform in Vietnam.

We remember the 3,000 Australians wounded, and the 523 Australians who paid the ultimate sacrifice.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We committed to closing the gender pay gap and that's what we're doing.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We want Australia to make more things here.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I still know my Yeppen from my Yeppoon. Kicked off the Bush Summit in Townsville with a Queenslander quiz from Chris Jones.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
✅ Requiring large companies to report their gender pay gap.

✅ Delivering pay rises for feminised industries like aged care and child care.

✅ Making it easier to raise award wages that have been undervalued on the basis of gender.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our bill also delivers paid prac for teaching, nursing, midwifery and social work students.

And we're helping more Australians access fee-free uni ready courses.

Education changes lives. We want to make it more affordable for Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Welcome home, our Olympic champions 🇦🇺
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description: Today we approved Australia’s biggest renewable energy project ever.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The incredible Labor Inner West team are all nominated and ready to go.

Our communities need good services. We need local infrastructure. We need good financial management.

That's what the Labor team have been doing - getting things done for local people and our community.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I pay tribute to my friend Prime Minister Fumio Kishida. He has always valued the vital relationship between Japan and Australia, and his leadership has helped strengthen it. I wish him all the very best for the future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description:
Australia’s most successful ever Olympic Games 🇦🇺

18 🥇 
19 🥈
16 🥉

And so many more special moments. 

Australia is so proud of our @ausolympicteam athletes. 👏
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
President-elect Prabowo, you are very welcome in Australia. 

I am pleased we have concluded our bilateral treaty-level Defence Cooperation Agreement.  

The friendship and partnership between our two great nations has never been stronger, or more important. 🇦🇺🇮🇩
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: The gender pay gap has just dropped to an historic low.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We have the sunlight, the space, the critical minerals, the skilled workers, the great universities and TAFEs, the trade ties to the fastest growing region of the world, in human history. 

The only thing our nation does not have is time to waste.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Welcome back to Australia, Prime Minister @chrisluxonmp. Australia and New Zealand are closer than friends – we are family. 🇦🇺🇳🇿
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description: BREAKING: We’ve just introduced legislation to pay super on paid parental leave.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Stop scrolling if you’ve got student debt.

We just introduced our bill to wipe $3 billion of it.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Australia stands with the United States, Egypt, and Qatar in pressing for a ceasefire in Gaza.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description:
We’re helping Australians get home safer and faster.

21 sets of traffic lights. Bypassed.
Up to 40 mins of travel time. Gone.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The Torrens to Darlington Project – the final piece of the North South Corridor in Adelaide – will create 5500 jobs a year while it’s being built.

And it will make travel safer, faster and easier for Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description:
The 18th of August holds a special meaning for Australia's Vietnam veterans. 

Today marks 58 years since the bloody battle that was Long Tan.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Tracey Roberts, our Member for Pearce, has been working to help her community with the cost of living every day.

It was a delight to meet some of the people she’s fighting for in WA this evening.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today we thank every one of our Vietnam veterans. And we say again that we are sorry it took us so long as a nation to do so. 

Lest we forget.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Wonderful celebration of the growing relationship between Australia and India at tonight’s India Australia Business and Community Alliance dinner in the Great Hall of Parliament House 🇦🇺🇮🇳 

Honoured to be the first PM to attend the event which gets bigger each year.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We call on all parties to agree to the deal.

Any delay will only see more lives lost. The human suffering is unacceptable.

Civilians must be protected, hostages must be released, and aid must flow.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And with a cap on fees we're also keeping costs down. 

Good for workers. Good for kids. Good for families. Good for the economy.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Too often, women suffer because their pain gets dismissed and goes undiagnosed.

We're changing that by opening specialist clinics, because women deserve better care.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Gold 🥇Silver 🥈and Bronze 🥉for Australia!! 🇦🇺 

Congratulations Arisa Trew!! Gold at 14 years old. 🥇🛹

Jack Robinson who claimed silver in men’s surfing! 🥈🏄‍♂️ 

And to Matt Glaetzer, Leigh Hoffman and Matt Richardson who won bronze in the team sprint 🥉🚴‍♂️🚴‍♂️🚴‍♂️.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We're extending paid parental leave to six months.

Because we'll aways support working families and work towards gender equality.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Charlie Senior and Caitlin Parker both claimed bronze medals in the boxing. Caitlin won Australia’s first medal ever in women’s boxing 👏

And there’s more medal opportunities to come this weekend. Go @ausolympicteam 🇦🇺
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: New album just dropped.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Incredibly inspiring, you’ve done Australia proud 🇦🇺
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
➡️ Helping with the cost of living.
➡️ Paying super on paid parental leave.
➡️ Wiping $3 billion of student debt.
➡️ Protecting women and children from deepfakes.
➡️ Creating secure jobs with a Future Made in Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description: Made a special call to our incredible @AUSOlympicTeam in Paris this arvo.

biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description:
1. Death penalty for convicted  Paedophiles or at a minimum 100years prison no parole.

2. Abolish welcome to country ceremony’s

3.End all DEI hiring

4. Abolish many of the useless government bodies that cost the tax payer a fortune.

biography: The problem with socialism is that you eventually run out of other peoples' money.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I'm not the only one excited about our latest announcement.

We're increasing wages for early childhood educators by 15%.

Higher wages for educators means better care for our young ones. 

And we’re doing this while keeping costs down for families by capping child care fees.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
More Aussies who have done us proud. 

Moesha Johnson claimed silver in the 10km marathon swim. 

Our men’s K4 won silver in a photo finish.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
More medals for our Aussie champs!

Meg Harris 🥈 has claimed silver in 50m freestyle, Nicola Olyslagers🥈 and Eleanor Patterson🥉 will take the podium together for the High Jump, and our spectacular swimmers have taken silver in the medley relay🥈!
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
My government’s first priority is the safety and security of Australians.

When the temperature of the security environment is rising, we must lower the temperature of debate.

Because our words and our actions matter.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
From the teachers in the school to cochlear implant specialists, the workers here at Macquarie Park represent the possibility of a better future for so many Australians.  

Building a future made in Australia means we can bring the benefits to all Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We're giving child care workers a 15% pay rise.

And keeping fees down for families.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Noemie Fox is Australia’s latest GOLD MEDALLIST after an incredible performance in the Kayak Cross.🥇👏

biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: So pleased to announce Renee Coffey as our Labor candidate for Griffith.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Renee is exactly who we need in Parliament – someone who will stand up for the values of her community, and who will deliver real change.

Getting more housing built, acting on climate change, making child care cheaper, and delivering cost of living relief.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The Cowra Breakout was the Second World War’s biggest mass prisoner-of-war escape.

Four Australian soldiers and 234 Japanese lost their lives.

Eighty years on from that fateful night, it was an honour to lay a wreath and pay my respects here.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description: Double Gold for Jess Fox. An Aussie Olympic legend. 🥇🇦🇺🛶🥇

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our Aussie athletes have had another huge day in Paris. 

Matt Ebden and John Peers are bringing home the gold in tennis for Australia for the first time since 1996 🎾🥇.

Grae Morris has claimed silver in windsurfing 🥈with Ariarne Titmus doing the same in the 800m freestyle 🥈.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: And Kaylee McKeown adds to her impressive haul with a bronze in the 200m individual medley 🥉and as part of the incredible team to claim bronze in the mixed medley relay 🥉.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I'm so pleased our Government has helped fund a new Shepherd Centre here in Sydney’s southwest. 

It will help so many families to have a better future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Good government looks after people, and it makes a real difference for people. 

We invested in this NextSense centre because it's helping Australians who have hearing or vision impairment lead full lives.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
To close the gaps in health, education and justice, we need to work together on a new way forward.

Side by side, we'll build the better future First Nations people need and deserve.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The workers here at the new Coles facility in Kemps Creek are working hard to get food on shelves every day. 

And they’re using new technology that makes Australia a world leader in distribution.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Getting more renewables up and running will bring power prices down. That's just a fact.

While we're getting on with it, Peter Dutton wants Australians to pay the price for his expensive nuclear plan.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We'll keep building an Australia where no-one is held back and no-one is left behind.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: You can call the National Referral Centre on 1800 954 610 to get more information and sign up.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: A quick note from me.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: My message to Australian citizens and residents in Lebanon is now is the time to leave.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our movement is about delivering a better life for working people.

And we’ll keep working every day to build it. 

We’ll keep working to build more homes. 

We’ll keep working to deliver more fee-free TAFE places.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
New ministry, same focus: helping with the cost of living.

We know Australians are under pressure.

That’s why we‘ve wasted no time going from the swearing-in of our new ministers to the first meeting of our new ministry.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: 🫶🥇🇦🇺 Jess Fox - what a legend.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We work together, we listen to each other and we act with purpose.

When team members step down that creates an opportunity for others to step up. 

My team is ready. And we're focused on continuing to deliver for Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We're wiping $3 billion in student debt for more than 3 million Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Every year, Australia's biggest gathering of Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander people happens here at the Garma Festival.

Garma gives us the chance to share in tens of thousands of years of knowledge, culture and tradition. And it asks us to be ambitious for the future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our commitment to a better future for First Nations people is as strong as ever.

We can close the gap. And we must.

We're building more remote housing, helping communities get the health care they need, and fully funding NT public schools.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Statement on the passing of Tom Pritchard.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I know she will continue to advocate for Tasmanians and fight for all Australians as a Senator, and we're all sending her support.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: These Aussie champions keep striking Gold! Congratulations to Saya Sakakibara 🚴🥇, Kaylee McKeown 🏊‍♀️🥇, and Cam McEvoy 🏊🥇.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’ll keep working to get wages moving.

We’ll keep working to deliver cheaper and cleaner renewable energy. 

To strengthen Medicare. To deliver cheaper child care. To make our future here in Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
From tax cuts, to cheaper child care, to power bill relief, to cheaper medicines and more homes for Australians, we've been working every day to change the lives of Australians.

We're a party of progress. And that means our work is never done.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Keeping costs down for families and getting wages up for workers. 

That’s what paying our childhood educators fairly and capping child care centre fees will mean.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re getting things done:
✅Give everyone a tax cut
✅Wiping $3 billion in student debt
✅Make medicines cheaper
✅Taking $300 off power bills
✅2.6million award wage workers getting pay rise
✅Adding superannuation to paid parental leave
✅Increasing Rent Assistance (again)
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
It will make a real difference to millions of people - from the check-out to the kitchen table.

Good, secure jobs out here in Western Sydney. And fully stocked shelves in all our suburbs.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
If you’ve got kids at school and no NBN at home, this post is for you.

We’ve now helped 15,000 families connect to the internet for free, and yours could be next.

We know getting the best education means getting online, and we’re giving more students that opportunity.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This is life changing. Shepherd Centres give children with hearing difficulties the support they need early on. 

Katia showed me how her cochlear implant works, and told me about the difference it makes to her life.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We want investment in renewable energy to create new jobs and bring real economic security to remote communities. 

Together with Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander people, we're determined to find a new way forward.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: ANNOUNCING: We will work with traditional owners to make Jabiluka part of Kakadu National Park, so it will be protected always.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
That means Jabiluka will never be mined. The Mirrar people have loved and cared for their land for more than 60,000 years. 

Our Government will work with them to keep it safe for all time.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I want to thank @SenCarolBrown for all her work as Assistant Minister for Infrastructure and Transport as she steps back from the role to prioritise her health.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
There is no impact to critical infrastructure, government services or Triple-0 services at this stage. 

The National Coordination Mechanism has been activated and is meeting now.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I am proud to lead a talented and united cabinet government that is focused every day on continuing to deliver better outcomes and more opportunities for all Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: A huge day for our Aussie Olympians in Paris - three gold medals, two silvers, putting us on top of the medal table. 🇦🇺
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Brendan’s work on TAFE and training has changed lives. 

He has created hundreds of thousands of fee-free TAFE places and secured the first National Skills Agreement in a decade.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia’s Local Hero winner at the Australian of the Year awards David Elliott and his wife Judy founded the natural history museum more than 20 years ago. 

Today, it's part of the awesome attractions that make outback Queensland a destination for people around the world.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
More jobs, higher wages and lower taxes.

We’re working hard to help Australians get ahead.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Most importantly, he’s given so many Australians the new skills and self-confidence to find a job they love.

You could not ask for a better colleague than Brendan O’Connor and you will not find a more decent human being.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This museum in Winton, Queensland is Australia’s very own Jurassic Park.

The Age of Dinosaurs is home to the most significant collection of fossils from our largest dinosaurs.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And she’ll help deliver more jobs for the local community, through projects like the Port of Townsville channel upgrade we visited today.

Edwina has raised her family here, worked to support locals here, and she’ll always put this community first.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Joint statement on the need for an urgent ceasefire in Gaza and the risk of expanded conflict between Hizballah and Israel.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And our tax cuts that came into effect on 1 July mean more money in your pocket.

We know families are looking for relief, and our changes will make a real difference.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Linda and Brendan have worked hard every day to build a better future for Australia. I can’t thank them enough.

I will be announcing new appointments on Sunday.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Jess Fox and Eddie Ockenden are veteran Olympians and incredible athletes, and they’ll do Australia proud as @AUSOlympicTeam flag bearers. Well done @jessfoxcanoe and @eddieockenden 🇦🇺
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Taking pressure off families is a core part of my Labor Government’s work. 

Last year we increased the child care subsidy, saving families thousands of dollars a year. 

We're expanding paid parental leave to six months by 2026, as well as adding paid superannuation.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Quick reminder - check your payslip.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

description: Gold! Congratulations to our 4x200m freestyle Olympic champions Mollie O’Callaghan, Lani Pallister, Brianna Throssell and Ariarne Titmus 🥇🇦🇺🏊‍♀️
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I look forward to welcoming Their Majesties King Charles III and Queen Camilla to Australia in October this year.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I understand Australians are concerned about the outage that is unfolding globally and affecting a wide range of services. 

My Government is working closely with the National Cyber Security Coordinator.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Australia remains steadfast in our commitment to seeking truth, justice and accountability from those responsible for this horrific act of violence.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We remember them today and our hearts go out to all those who knew them best and loved them most. The people for whom this anniversary brings a new reminder of irreplaceable loss.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Ten years ago the world was shaken by the terrible news that Malaysian Airlines flight MH17 had been shot from the skies. 

All 298 passengers and crew on board that day lost their lives, including 38 people who called Australia home.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Delighted to welcome Prime Minister Feleti Teo of Tuvalu to Australia. 

We discussed the Falepili Union our countries signed last year, and ways to promote peace and security in our Pacific region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Under Labor, every Australian taxpayer just got a tax cut. Under the Liberals, people on the lowest incomes would have got nothing.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: In a Labor Government, Ali will fight for that future and fight for the people of Dickson every day.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The people of Dickson know Ali France well. 

A local Mum and a world champion para-athlete, she’s a courageous fighter.

Ali and her family have experienced first-hand the importance of Medicare and the NDIS.

I’m so proud that she’s running as Labor’s Candidate for Dickson.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
In good times or hard, Rebecca Hack is the kind of person you want in your corner.

And we’ve just announced that she’ll be Labor’s Candidate for Ryan.

She’s a Toowong local, a teacher and a dedicated member of her community.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Ali knows our focus needs to be on helping with the cost of living, not on expensive nuclear energy.

We’re getting on with delivering cheaper, cleaner energy now – like with the Supernode BESS project which will be one of Australia's biggest batteries.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Madonna Jarrett is determined to deliver real progressive change for her community.

As a Brisbane local she’s worked with people from all over the country to tackle housing affordability, women’s equality, and homelessness.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Linda Burney and Brendan O’Connor have made an outstanding contribution to our nation.

Today, they have announced they will retire at the next election. They will also step down as Ministers.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today we dropped in to Loganlea TAFE and heard from locals about how fee-free TAFE is changing lives. 

With Rowan on our team, we’ll continue to deliver for Forde with cost of living relief, affordable housing and secure jobs.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Working with our Labor Government, Rebecca Hack will help tackle the things that matter: housing, cost of living, and climate change. She’s ready to be a strong voice for her community in Canberra.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
There is no place for violence, hatred or discrimination of any kind in Australia. 

And as part of my Government's work to promote social cohesion, we have appointed Jillian Segal AO as Special Envoy to combat Antisemitism.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Right now communities are distressed. People have been targeted for who they are. As leaders, we need to foster the unity and cohesion and diversity that has always been our nation’s greatest strength.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We are working every day to help Australians with the cost of living.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Our social cohesion has been built over the course of generations by people of all backgrounds and from every faith and tradition. All of us take pride in it, all of us must work together to protect it.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Now the stats are in: more than two million extra appointments have been fully bulk-billed, with close to a million in May alone.

On top of that, our free Medicare Urgent Care Clinics have just notched up 500,000 visits.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Local governments are the lifeblood of Australia’s cities, towns and regions. 

The work they do in communities across our country should be recognised and celebrated.

I was delighted to present the National Awards for Local Government with Minister Kristy McBain tonight.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Here's an update for the next time there's a cut, burn or sprain. 

Already, 500,000 Australians have visited a free Medicare Urgent Care Clinic.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Powerful daylist 💡🎧

Starting this month, we're rolling out $300 off power bills for every Australian household.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We are focused on delivering cost of living relief that makes a difference for Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And I’m so proud to announce her as Labor’s Candidate for Brisbane. 

Madonna knows that to get big things done you need to do more than talk about the issues - you need to deliver. 

I know that as part of our Labor team, she’ll be working for Brisbane every day.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Working with local governments, we can get important things done.

With representatives from every council across Australia in Canberra this week, that's what we're doing.

We’re providing important funding to help them deliver services that matter to you.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’ve opened 58 clinics, with 29 more on the way - including this one here in Queanbeyan, NSW.

We’re making it easier to see a doctor for free.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This afternoon I was pleased to speak with new UK Prime Minister @Keir_Starmer.

We have a lot to work on together as we grow our economies, advance AUKUS, and seize the opportunities of the global clean energy transformation.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Getting health care should rely on your Medicare card, not your credit card.

That's why we tripled the bulk-billing incentive, helping GPs see more patients for free.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And five million Australians have saved money with cheaper medicines.

Labor built Medicare and we're working hard to strengthen it.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: How it started vs. how it's going
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Edwina Andrew knows first-hand what it’s like to do it tough, and now she works to help others facing disadvantage.

As Labor’s Candidate for Herbert, Edwina will be a strong voice in the Labor team that's rolling out help with the cost of living.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Thank you for your leadership and ongoing service President Biden. The Australia-US Alliance has never been stronger with our shared commitment to democratic values, international security, economic prosperity and climate action for this and future generations.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We're working every day to ensure Australians are earning more, and keeping more of what they earn.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Congratulations to my friend and new UK Prime Minister @Keir_Starmer on his resounding election victory - I look forward to working constructively with the incoming @UKLabour Government
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I'm honoured to belong to a movement and lead a party that is home to true believers like the ones we celebrated tonight.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
While in Kyiv in 2022, I had the chance to pay my respects at the memorial to the Australian victims.  

These were travellers heading home. Young families, lifelong partners, retirees returning from trips they’d long planned, grandchildren alongside their devoted grandfather.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Peter Dutton won't give his nuclear reactor plan a price tag - but he knows it'll be a big bill.

We're working on getting your power bills down right now - with cheap, clean renewable energy.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Cost of living relief for every Australian in every part of the country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We also discussed the international strategic outlook, including conflict in the Middle East and Russia’s illegal invasion of Ukraine.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Australia, meet your new Governor-General, Her Excellency the Honourable Ms Sam Mostyn AC.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Our Paralympic athletes are ready. 

They've been putting in the early mornings and long sessions, and soon they will be at the pinnacle of world sport.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Today more than 2.6 million Australians got a pay rise.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The Future Made in Australia Act will mean:
✅ More secure, well-paid jobs for Australians
✅ Building the technology of the future
✅ Quality Australian products to be proud of
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Just like the desserts here at Sweet Magic, our tax cuts will hit the sweet spot.

Cost of living relief for every taxpayer, while taking pressure off inflation.

Wonderful meet the lovely staff at Sweet Magic in Truganina this morning.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We've just introduced our bill to make more things here at home.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The incident at former President Trump’s campaign event in Pennsylvania today is concerning and confronting. There is no place for violence in the democratic process.

I am relieved to hear reports that former President Trump is now safe.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
92% of the global economy is signed up to Net Zero.

We want to make sure that every community in Australia benefits from the opportunities of a clean energy future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: I want Aussie kids today to be the gold medal winners of the future, and this will help make that happen.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Chatting with the wonderful locals and business owners in Forest Hill in Melbourne’s east with local state MP John Mullahy. Always time for a quick banh mi and a coffee! 🥖☕️
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Soon we will also be appointing a Special Envoy to combat Islamophobia. 

All of us have a responsibility to prevent conflict in the Middle East from being used as a platform for prejudice here at home.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This is Rowan Holzberger, our Labor candidate for Forde.

Rowan raised his family here. He knows this community like the back of his hand, having worked in farming, construction, and small business.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And we are proud to back them – we've doubled the government's funding for Paralympic sport, the biggest ever increase. 

Good luck in Paris - the nation will be cheering you on.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia and Solomon Islands are close friends and partners.

Today, Prime Minister Jeremiah Manele visited Canberra. 

It was an opportunity for us to discuss our connected future, and to strengthen our partnership.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Mark your calendars. 🗓️

Cost of living relief is coming to every household on Monday.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Grace Tame is an inspiration.

Using her voice to stand up for survivors of child sexual abuse, she’s continuing to make a real difference.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I love Aussie music.

So when two of my Hottest 100 picks, Budjerah and Lime Cordiale, came to Canberra I couldn't miss a chance to say hello!
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Save the date.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Taking pressure off parents is at the heart of our cheaper child care and increased paid parental leave policies. 

I heard from Georgie Dent at The Parenthood about how our changes are making a difference to families right across the country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: It was an honour to stand by his side in Kyiv and assure him that Australia stands with Ukraine. My sincere condolences to Stefan's family, friends and all who will mourn his loss. May he rest in peace.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: From economic growth and skills sharing to the stability of our region, Australia looks forward to working with Solomon Islands into the future.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
It will mean Team Australia has extra doctors, physios and staff to give our Aussie athletes the best chance at winning gold. 

And it comes on top of our government’s record investment of $283m in elite sport over the next two years. 

The countdown is on – only 27 days to go!
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re giving our Olympic and Paralympic athletes a grand send-off to Paris. 

The Prime Minister’s Olympic Dinner raises funds that go direct to our athletes, coaches and support staff.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Upgraded training facilities, the best coaching and support staff, and financial support will all make a difference.

And we're making a record investment in our Paralympic athletes, because they deserve the best.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This business in southeast Melbourne grows nearly 14 million plants a year. 

And on Monday nearly 14 million Australians will get a tax cut. 

Local MP Cassandra Fernando spoke to the workers at JD Propagation about how our tax cuts will make a huge difference.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: We're focused on cutting taxes, growing wages and helping families with the cost of living because we want an economy where every Australian can thrive.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Earlier tonight I was pleased to speak with Julian Assange to welcome him home to his family in Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This is the culmination of careful, patient and determined work.

It is another example of why mature, calibrated and consistent engagement is the best way to get results in Australia’s national interest.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Cate Campbell is an Australian Olympic champion.

Today she joined me as we announced funding to set the next generation of Olympic and Paralympic athletes up for success.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: And working alongside people like Bruce and Denise, we’re committed to doing what it takes.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
As Prime Minister, I have been clear – regardless of what you think of his activities, Mr Assange’s case had dragged on for too long.

I have clearly and consistently – at every opportunity and at every level – advocated for Mr Assange’s case to be concluded.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The National Gallery of Australia has always showcased our greatest artists, and brought the world’s finest art to our shores. 

I'll always support the arts. Tonight I opened the gallery's newest exhibition, Gauguin’s World: Tōna Iho, Tōna Ao.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Good secure jobs in Tassie today, cheap, clean power for Australia tomorrow

These Marinus Link workers I ran into this morning know that Australia’s future will be powered by renewables.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: In two weeks, we're taking $300 off your power bills. In two decades, Peter Dutton will serve up the most expensive form of energy there is.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: The sudden passing of Stefan Romaniw is very sad news. Stefan's commitment to the cause of peace and his steadfast support for the people of Ukraine were an inspiration and an example to so many Australians.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The Australian Government has consistently said that Mr. Assange’s case has dragged on for too long, and that there is nothing to be gained by his continued incarceration.

We want him brought home to Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: The official portrait of Governor-General David Hurley will stand as a testament to his commitment to supporting Australians in the wake of devastating bushfires, and as a tribute to a remarkable life of service.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: On 1 July cost of living relief is coming to every household in Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Welcome to the team, Senator Lisa Darmanin. 

Lisa is a lifelong advocate for working women, for equal pay and for action on domestic violence. 

I know Lisa will continue to make a positive difference in her new role as a Senator for Victoria.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We're making the code mandatory. That means heavy fines for serious breaches of the rules.

And helping farmers speak up when they’re not getting a fair deal.

We want to make sure Australians aren’t paying more than they should.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: That’s where our focus is. Helping with the cost of living for every Australian.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re cracking down on the big supermarkets to give Australians better prices at the checkout. 

Right now, the code of conduct covering supermarkets is voluntary. Too often, that means families and farmers aren't getting a fair go.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We're investing in nationally important infrastructure like this right across the country.

It's how we're building a future made in Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: 5 things that will help with the cost of living from 1 July.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Giselle’s got a good excuse to be late for school this morning.

She’s just been awarded National Volunteer of the Year by the Juvenile Diabetes Research Foundation.

At just 14, her advocacy is making a difference for people living with Type 1 Diabetes.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Here in Perth, along with Chinese Premier Li Qiang, we celebrated the incredible contributions that Chinese-Australians have made to Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
In just 10 days time, every Australian gets a tax cut. 

Whether you live in Perth or Penrith, Darwin or Devonport – from 1 July everyone will keep more of what they earn. 

📷 chatting with @mjrowland68 this morning from Tasmania.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
As a former NSW Treasurer and Minister for Energy and Environment, Matt knows renewables are the cheapest form of new energy.

In his new role, I know he'll work tirelessly as part of the authority that provides expert advice to government.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Australia is proudly home to 1.4 million people of Chinese ancestry. 

They're an important part of our national story, and an integral part of our national identity.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The Daniel Morcombe Foundation’s work has made an important difference, but there’s more to do together.

With the states and territories, our ambitious goal is to end violence against women and children in a generation.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: The energy carried by all who come here with the greatest of aspirations - to make a new life for themselves and their families - is an energy that has made Australia a better nation for us all.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Today Australian and Chinese business leaders came together in Perth to discuss new ways to collaborate and seize the opportunities of the future. 

We can achieve so much more when we work together.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: By acting on climate change, we'll deliver cheaper, cleaner energy and more secure jobs.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
What a spectacular view. 

The workers here at the Port of Burnie bring Tasmanian resources to the world while boosting the local economy.

And thanks to a Federal Government investment, this new machine will load ships at twice the rate of the old one.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
The upgrades also mean it will remain a centre of women’s sport, with funding for new female-friendly change rooms.

We’re making sure Leichhardt Oval is enjoyed by the community for decades to come.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Trade supports one in four Australian jobs. And with China our biggest trading partner, stabilising our relationship matters. 

The recent removal of trade barriers is already making a difference for Australian families, workers and businesses.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Thanks for the chat, Susan and Stephen.

We're making sure more Australians can get the medicine they need, without worrying about the cost.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
For kids like Huxley, Archie, Hailey and Colleen, child care is all about learning and having fun.

For parents it’s about giving your children the best start in life.

Our cheaper child care policy is helping families do just that.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Dorna came here as a refugee from Iran. She’s made Australia her home, and she's contributing to our community. 

Today, she told me she’s landed her dream job.

Dorna’s earning a Certificate II in Baking while working here at The Bread and Butter Project.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Eid Mubarak.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: BREAKING: I'm appointing Matt Kean as the next Chair of the Climate Change Authority.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: A look behind the scenes of hosting Chinese Premier Li Qiang at Parliament House.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
And there’s nothing better than the feeling of community you get sitting on Wayne Pearce Hill.

That’s why we’ve teamed up with the Inner West Council and the @ChrisMinnsMP Government to renovate the oval.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I condemn the attack on the electorate office of Josh Burns. Those responsible should face the full force of the law. 

This is a serious attack. The targeting of a Jewish MP is very distressing. 

There is no place for political violence in Australia.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Every kid deserves the best start in life. 

Our cheaper child care means more families have access to quality early education for their kids.

It has made a difference for families and children in every part of the country.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Along with the resumption of high-level economic dialogue, these are important steps toward a more stable relationship and a more secure region.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
We’re saving Leichhardt Oval.

This historic oval is a home to many - from the Wests Tigers and Sydney FC, to school teams and local clubs. 

The sporting dreams of so many young players begin right here.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
I’m pleased to announce the Premier of the People’s Republic of China, Li Qiang, will visit Australia next week.

Australia continues to pursue a stable and direct relationship with China. This visit is an opportunity to engage directly on key issues for both our nations.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
“They’ve helped me a lot,” she told me.

The Bread and Butter Project aren’t just making delicious croissants – they’re changing lives.

And we’re so proud to support their important work.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: This morning I welcomed Giselle to Kirribilli House to say congratulations.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
That's thanks to the new Flinders University Health and Medical Research Building, which opens today.

The research done in this building will save lives.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
Some of these Kincumber Roos will be the Central Coast Mariners of tomorrow.

So I couldn’t be more pleased to say hello as we checked in on the upgrades to the home of the Kincumber Roos Soccer Club.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Welcome to Canberra, Premier Li Qiang 🇦🇺🇨🇳
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
In less than three weeks:
➡️ $300 off energy bills for every household.
➡️ Tax cuts for every Australian tax payer.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description:
This is what a future made in Australia looks like: Australian research making all the difference for people at home and across the world.

I'm excited to see what breakthroughs the team here will make.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Today Chinese Premier Li Qiang and I signed agreements to further our collaboration on climate action, education, culture, and to enhance our Free Trade Agreement.
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: It’s now clear Peter Dutton is a risk to jobs and a risk to action on climate change 👇👇
biography: Prime Minister of Australia. Member for Grayndler. Authorised by Anthony Albanese, ALP, Canberra.

name: Anthony Albanese
description: Always good to talk with you as leader of the world’s largest democracy - much work to do enhancing our Strategic Partnership and with the Quad 🇦🇺🇮🇳
